 da imaju na zajedništvo.

846
00:40:33,520 --> 00:40:35,400
 i jako je teško i nezgodno,

847
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:37,120
 zapravo sigurno će to bolje reći

848
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:39,280
 iz prve ruke roditelji koji gore odgajaju djecu,

849
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:41,580
 ali vjerujte mi

850
00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:43,980
 da oni koji dovode djecu u crkvu,

851
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:48,160
 da u nas u crkvi mogu naučiti samo dobre i pozitivne stvari.

852
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:51,180
 Ali, problem je,

853
00:40:51,180 --> 00:40:52,860
 evo reći mi u jednoj školi,

854
00:40:52,860 --> 00:40:54,100
 u San Galenu,

855
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:55,660
 vjerovali li ne,

856
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:56,860
 musliman predajver u nauk.

857
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:59,080
 Baš neobično,

858
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,900
 ali događaju se takve stvari,

859
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:02,500
 skroz čudne,

860
00:41:02,500 --> 00:41:04,660
 i onda u vrtićima,

861
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:06,840
 pristupio mi je čovjek s problemom,

862
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,340
 kaže on,

863
00:41:07,340 --> 00:41:09,960
 moj dijete u vrtiću mora ići na jogu.

864
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:11,680
 Molim,

865
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:13,320
 strašno,

866
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,600
 strašno.

867
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,600
 A evo i među ostalog,

868
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:18,920
 mi imamo u prostorijama svojim crkvenim,

869
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:19,580
 imamo spor,

870
00:41:19,580 --> 00:41:20,260
 probu spora,

871
00:41:20,260 --> 00:41:21,700
 pored nas je joga.

872
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:24,740
 Teško je,

873
00:41:24,740 --> 00:41:27,020
 ali ako mi odustanemo,

874
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:29,020
 znači da zlo pobjeđuje,

875
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:32,420
 tako da jedina opcija je borba.

876
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:36,740
 Molitva, molitva, molitva i zajedništvo.

877
00:41:36,740 --> 00:41:38,520
 Evo, to je nešto što je jako važno,

878
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,360
 i znači mu nastajem,

879
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:43,520
 evo sam kao svećenik prudanijeti svoje zajednici,

880
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:45,460
 a da je lako, nije ni malo lako,

881
00:41:45,460 --> 00:41:47,700
 i zaista, zaista čujem

882
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:50,500
 od brojnih takve iskustva,

883
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:52,360
 evo, već je mu u stariju školi,

884
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:53,380
 u vrtićima je tako,

885
00:41:53,380 --> 00:41:54,700
 onda, što se još događa,

886
00:41:54,700 --> 00:41:56,100
 ono što čujete na televiziji,

887
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,520
 ili od drugih,

888
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:59,360
 kako djeca mora dolaziti,

889
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:00,880
 jedan u školu,

890
00:42:00,880 --> 00:42:01,960
 obučeni kao muškar,

891
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:02,820
 drugu kao žene,

892
00:42:02,820 --> 00:42:03,940
 to je sve istina,

893
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:05,040
 to se sve događa.

894
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:08,060
 i kad iz prve ruke je to vidiš,

895
00:42:08,060 --> 00:42:09,620
 to je jako tužno i žalosno,

896
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:12,940
 ali drago mi da se naši ljudi svjesni te poteškoće,

897
00:42:12,940 --> 00:42:14,740
 ako si ti svjestan problema,

898
00:42:14,740 --> 00:42:16,480
 onda ga se nemoj bojati.

899
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:18,940
 Ja kažem čovjeku,

900
00:42:18,940 --> 00:42:21,240
 blagoslovi svoje dijete pri odlaska u vrtić,

901
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:22,340
 i on je onda intervenirao

902
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:22,780
 i rekli su,

903
00:42:22,780 --> 00:42:26,280
 ok, dijete ne mora biti u programu jogi,

904
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,420
 bit će u drugoj prostoriji,

905
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:29,060
 ali sam je taj prostor,

906
00:42:29,060 --> 00:42:30,440
 naravno, ako se to država joga,

907
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,880
 pa čovječe,

908
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,940
 ja kad dođem u Hercegovornu,

909
00:42:33,940 --> 00:42:34,840
 ja prodišem,

910
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,640
 ja gledam reći,

911
00:42:36,640 --> 00:42:39,020
 kao što u Međugorju,

912
00:42:39,020 --> 00:42:39,820
 kad dođeš,

913
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:40,920
 udišeš tu svetost,

914
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,660
 jer ona je u zraku,

915
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:42,400
 ona je u okruženju,

916
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:43,240
 ona je u prostoru,

917
00:42:43,240 --> 00:42:44,000
 Boži duh,

918
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:44,640
 sve,

919
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:46,580
 sve obuhvaća,

920
00:42:46,580 --> 00:42:48,080
 a tako i na džavoski.

921
00:42:49,180 --> 00:42:50,380
 Ako mu se mi klanjamo,

922
00:42:50,380 --> 00:42:50,900
 naravno,

923
00:42:50,900 --> 00:42:53,180
 i zato mi blagoslivljamo naše kuće

924
00:42:53,180 --> 00:42:55,260
 i da nam Boži duh dođe,

925
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:56,880
 da bude prisutan na našim domovima.

926
00:42:56,880 --> 00:43:00,020
 I naravno da je poteškoća,

927
00:43:00,020 --> 00:43:01,560
 tu je joga u toj prostoriji

928
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:02,500
 i ti ulaziš tu.

929
00:43:02,500 --> 00:43:03,680
 Naravno da nije ugodno,

930
00:43:03,680 --> 00:43:04,280
 naravno da nije dobro,

931
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:05,240
 ja govorim blagoslovi,

932
00:43:05,240 --> 00:43:07,260
 izmoli zašto nad svojim djetetom,

933
00:43:07,260 --> 00:43:08,600
 ako nemaš drugog rešenja,

934
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:09,500
 ako imaš pokušaj,

935
00:43:09,500 --> 00:43:11,100
 slati možda u neki drugi vrtić

936
00:43:11,100 --> 00:43:11,780
 ili negdje drugo.

937
00:43:12,500 --> 00:43:13,780
 Ja se nadam da će možda nekaj gore

938
00:43:13,780 --> 00:43:17,220
 i otvoriti se neke katoličke vrtići,

939
00:43:17,220 --> 00:43:18,500
 škole ili nešto takvo,

940
00:43:18,500 --> 00:43:19,340
 možda ima,

941
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:20,400
 nisam čuo,

942
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:23,680
 gdje će se širiti samo vjerska poruka,

943
00:43:23,680 --> 00:43:24,680
 poruka evanđelja.

944
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:27,760
 Ali evo, sad za sada situacija je teška,

945
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:29,940
 u školama imaju muški vjese,

946
00:43:29,940 --> 00:43:31,040
 ženski vjese i srednji.

947
00:43:31,040 --> 00:43:32,860
 I sad ti,

948
00:43:32,860 --> 00:43:34,220
 nažalost,

949
00:43:34,220 --> 00:43:35,900
 meni je zaista žao,

950
00:43:35,900 --> 00:43:36,660
 žao,

951
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:39,780
 ali takva je situacija.

952
00:43:39,780 --> 00:43:40,760
 Stvarno je takva.

953
00:43:40,760 --> 00:43:42,180
 Ljudi gore idu

954
00:43:42,180 --> 00:43:43,000
 u potrazi

955
00:43:43,000 --> 00:43:45,800
 za nekim financijskim,

956
00:43:45,800 --> 00:43:47,420
 ajmo reći dobitom,

957
00:43:47,420 --> 00:43:48,800
 profitom,

958
00:43:48,800 --> 00:43:51,580
 ali izgube puno važnije stvari.

959
00:43:51,580 --> 00:43:52,620
 Tako da,

960
00:43:52,620 --> 00:43:54,460
 ako ne morate ljudi,

961
00:43:54,900 --> 00:43:56,160
 nemojte ići nigdje vani,

962
00:43:56,160 --> 00:43:57,160
 znači,

963
00:43:57,160 --> 00:43:59,940
 najbitnije je ono što u vašem životu,

964
00:43:59,940 --> 00:44:02,000
 što zapravo vas formira kao osobu,

965
00:44:02,000 --> 00:44:02,820
 samo gospodin.

966
00:44:02,820 --> 00:44:05,240
 Ne može vas formirati ni novac,

967
00:44:05,240 --> 00:44:06,140
 ni stan,

968
00:44:06,140 --> 00:44:07,100
 ni kuća,

969
00:44:07,100 --> 00:44:07,920
 ni tiko drugi.

970
00:44:07,920 --> 00:44:10,840
 Ako želite živjeti,

971
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:12,100
 slobodno živjeti,

972
00:44:12,100 --> 00:44:13,760
 evanđelje živjeti po Božijemu,

973
00:44:13,760 --> 00:44:15,020
 živjeti u miru,

974
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:16,720
 koji nam Hristus krsli donosi,

975
00:44:16,720 --> 00:44:17,980
 jednostavno,

976
00:44:17,980 --> 00:44:19,960
 ne trčimo za prolaznim dobima.

977
00:44:19,960 --> 00:44:22,840
 Znači, samo tražite na nebeska.

978
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:24,660
 Ne, još, vica ska je nekako,

979
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:26,160
 kao i cijela Evropa,

980
00:44:26,160 --> 00:44:28,900
 počupala svoje kršćanske korjene,

981
00:44:28,900 --> 00:44:30,200
 na kojima izrasla.

982
00:44:30,200 --> 00:44:32,880
 Na Švicarska ima i brojne svece,

983
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:35,160
 još, mi smo bili u svetište njihovog

984
00:44:35,160 --> 00:44:36,520
 nacionalnog zaštnjika.

985
00:44:36,520 --> 00:44:39,440
 Bruder Klaus il sveti Nikola von Fluev,

986
00:44:39,680 --> 00:44:44,740
 koliko velik svec, koliko je on sedamnijesil nešto godina živio samo u Neuharistiji.

987
00:44:44,840 --> 00:44:47,440
 Tako je, to je začuđujuće.

988
00:44:47,440 --> 00:44:49,400
 I kad su bili ratovi,

989
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,300
 ima tamo jedna freska u crkvi,

990
00:44:51,300 --> 00:44:55,720
 evo, baš smo nas dvojica išli kad si ti bio gore kod mene.

991
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:58,620
 Ja sam isto kada prvi put posjetio to svetište.

992
00:44:58,620 --> 00:45:03,000
 On je baš, baš, baš zanimljiv svetac.

993
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,740
 Bruder Klaus, kako ga zovu,

994
00:45:05,740 --> 00:45:07,340
 on je bio oženjen,

995
00:45:07,340 --> 00:45:08,820
 imao je desetara djece

996
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:11,980
 i odučio se posvetiti Bogu.

997
00:45:11,980 --> 00:45:14,700
 I naravno, crkva mu je dopustila,

998
00:45:14,700 --> 00:45:16,680
 kad su djeza stasala

999
00:45:16,680 --> 00:45:19,140
 i uz dopuštenje, naravno, njegove supruge,

1000
00:45:19,140 --> 00:45:20,920
 da posveti svoj život Bogu.

1001
00:45:20,920 --> 00:45:22,040
 Osituo je takav poziv.

1002
00:45:22,040 --> 00:45:24,520
 I živio je, evo, što si ti rekao,

1003
00:45:24,520 --> 00:45:26,760
 više od 15, među 15 i 20 godina,

1004
00:45:26,760 --> 00:45:27,560
 da sam ne znam točno,

1005
00:45:27,560 --> 00:45:29,380
 samo Deuharistije.

1006
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,320
 A sam mislite tu svetost.

1007
00:45:31,320 --> 00:45:32,540
 To je čudesno.

1008
00:45:32,540 --> 00:45:33,500
 Čudesno.

1009
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:36,740
 I kad smo bili u tom svetištu,

1010
00:45:37,480 --> 00:45:39,780
 mi smo očekivali sad, ti znaš kako su u nas svetišta,

1011
00:45:39,780 --> 00:45:41,640
 pogotovo tako, nekog velikog sveca,

1012
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:43,060
 očekuješ neku veliku crkvu,

1013
00:45:43,060 --> 00:45:46,800
 baš organizirano, okolo, sve lijepo, uredno,

1014
00:45:46,800 --> 00:45:48,320
 prostor za molitvu,

1015
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:50,300
 jedva smo našli, sjećaš se?

1016
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:52,560
 Blunjali smo po onim brdima,

1017
00:45:52,560 --> 00:45:54,920
 tražeći mala kolibica,

1018
00:45:54,920 --> 00:45:56,560
 evo, kažu, tu je,

1019
00:45:56,560 --> 00:45:58,580
 tu je, vidjeli smo ono kuću gdje on živio.

1020
00:45:58,580 --> 00:46:00,160
 Koliba je doslo imala dva prozora.

1021
00:46:00,160 --> 00:46:01,960
 Jedan koje gleda u crku,

1022
00:46:01,960 --> 00:46:03,900
 a koju smo ljudi napravili,

1023
00:46:03,900 --> 00:46:05,560
 drugi gdje je primao ljude.

1024
00:46:05,620 --> 00:46:07,180
 Tako je, tako je, jednostavno,

1025
00:46:07,180 --> 00:46:10,140
 nadam se, evo, da će se malo više proširiti štovanje

1026
00:46:10,140 --> 00:46:12,520
 prema tom velikom, velikom, velikom svecu,

1027
00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:14,240
 koji je, evo, ali njega zaista

1028
00:46:14,240 --> 00:46:16,520
 u Švicarskoj

1029
00:46:16,520 --> 00:46:18,380
 štuje narod, zaista ga štuje,

1030
00:46:18,380 --> 00:46:19,900
 ne onako kako bi trebao,

1031
00:46:19,900 --> 00:46:21,780
 ali oni koji su pobožni,

1032
00:46:21,780 --> 00:46:23,560
 mole se njemu zagovor,

1033
00:46:23,560 --> 00:46:25,420
 jer je veliki svetac,

1034
00:46:25,420 --> 00:46:27,540
 evo, švicarski nacionalni svetac,

1035
00:46:27,540 --> 00:46:29,720
 i oni vjeruju zaista da kroz njegove molitve,

1036
00:46:29,720 --> 00:46:31,580
 jer evo, kad je okolo buktio rat

1037
00:46:31,580 --> 00:46:32,840
 u svim državama Europi,

1038
00:46:33,200 --> 00:46:33,980
 oni su se molili,

1039
00:46:33,980 --> 00:46:35,840
 i zaista Švicarska nije, evo,

1040
00:46:35,840 --> 00:46:37,180
 dodirnuta, okrznuta,

1041
00:46:37,180 --> 00:46:40,020
 i ljudi vjeruju da je to njegov zagovor,

1042
00:46:40,020 --> 00:46:41,640
 tako da bio je veliki svetac,

1043
00:46:41,640 --> 00:46:42,660
 i evo,

1044
00:46:42,660 --> 00:46:44,180
 sveti Nikola,

1045
00:46:44,180 --> 00:46:45,600
 Bruder, Klause,

1046
00:46:45,600 --> 00:46:48,340
 moli se, evo, za sve nas,

1047
00:46:48,340 --> 00:46:50,660
 pozornost za svoj švicarski narod.

1048
00:46:50,660 --> 00:46:52,480
 Mi smo ovdje u Hercegni,

1049
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:54,800
 pa možda počesto i,

1050
00:46:54,800 --> 00:46:56,760
 nismo ni svjestni,

1051
00:46:56,760 --> 00:46:58,600
 a i pomalo i nezahvalni za sve ovo,

1052
00:46:58,600 --> 00:47:00,040
 što ovdje mi imamo,

1053
00:47:00,040 --> 00:47:01,740
 i ovo je, pa nekoj,

1054
00:47:01,740 --> 00:47:04,020
 duhovna privilegija sve što mi imamo,

1055
00:47:04,020 --> 00:47:06,480
 kad pogledamo to gore siromaštvo u Švicarskoj.

1056
00:47:07,360 --> 00:47:09,340
 Tako je, baš duhovna privilegija,

1057
00:47:09,340 --> 00:47:11,460
 to si jako, jako lijepo rekao,

1058
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,740
 ovaj, ali,

1059
00:47:12,740 --> 00:47:14,420
 tek kad odeš van, to shvatiš.

1060
00:47:14,420 --> 00:47:15,320
 Evo, ja prvi,

1061
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:18,640
 ja nisam razumio koliko je ovdje blago i ljepota,

1062
00:47:18,640 --> 00:47:19,580
 dok ne dođeš.

1063
00:47:19,580 --> 00:47:21,160
 I onda vidiš nekad,

1064
00:47:21,160 --> 00:47:22,380
 zašto i naši ljudi,

1065
00:47:22,380 --> 00:47:24,180
 ja da čekaju neka hodočašća,

1066
00:47:24,180 --> 00:47:25,700
 da malo pobjegnu,

1067
00:47:25,700 --> 00:47:27,940
 evo, ja prvi,

1068
00:47:27,940 --> 00:47:30,000
 sada, kad dođeš ovamo,

1069
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:31,540
 malo preko ljeta na odmor,

1070
00:47:31,540 --> 00:47:33,480
 i odeš u Međugorje,

1071
00:47:33,480 --> 00:47:35,100
 i sad susretiš te strance,

1072
00:47:36,120 --> 00:47:37,980
 međugorje ima trenut na evo sa gore živim.

1073
00:47:37,980 --> 00:47:40,220
 I tek sad svačaš,

1074
00:47:40,220 --> 00:47:41,920
 zašto je uopće

1075
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:44,200
 toliko ljudi tu u Međugorju?

1076
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:47,020
 Zašto su tolki brojni stranci došli?

1077
00:47:47,020 --> 00:47:48,620
 Ljudi su žedni Boga.

1078
00:47:48,620 --> 00:47:50,380
 Ljudi su žedni Boga,

1079
00:47:50,380 --> 00:47:52,760
 a gore je teško naći izvor.

1080
00:47:52,760 --> 00:47:54,680
 Ja zato se nadam

1081
00:47:54,680 --> 00:47:56,060
 da će se, evo,

1082
00:47:56,060 --> 00:47:58,740
 što više pokrenuti moletvenih zajednica,

1083
00:47:58,740 --> 00:48:00,580
 moletvenih skupina, grupa,

1084
00:48:00,580 --> 00:48:02,540
 frame, mladih, svih,

1085
00:48:02,540 --> 00:48:05,440
 jer kad se takve grupe ujedinjuju,

1086
00:48:05,620 --> 00:48:06,680
 kad vidi da ima nas više.

1087
00:48:06,680 --> 00:48:09,080
 Znaš, teško ti je nekad nešto,

1088
00:48:09,080 --> 00:48:11,340
 svi trče tamo gdje ima ljudi.

1089
00:48:11,340 --> 00:48:12,260
 Mi smo takvi.

1090
00:48:12,260 --> 00:48:14,200
 Ne bi niko sam nešto učinio,

1091
00:48:14,200 --> 00:48:15,680
 ne bi niko sam nešto pokrenuo.

1092
00:48:15,680 --> 00:48:17,160
 I onda je to nezgodno.

1093
00:48:17,160 --> 00:48:20,500
 A ovdje imaš, možeš izabrat ne samo u Hercegovini,

1094
00:48:20,500 --> 00:48:23,820
 Zagreb, pa imaš na izbor moletvenih zajednica,

1095
00:48:23,820 --> 00:48:25,080
 gdje ko želiš priključit se.

1096
00:48:25,080 --> 00:48:26,540
 A ako želiš rasti,

1097
00:48:26,540 --> 00:48:28,080
 odnosu zbog gospodina,

1098
00:48:28,080 --> 00:48:29,640
 naravno trebati odsobni odnos,

1099
00:48:30,200 --> 00:48:31,680
 ali zajednica je jako važna.

1100
00:48:31,680 --> 00:48:33,140
 Zajednica je jako važna.

1101
00:48:33,140 --> 00:48:36,620
 I evo, zato sam upravo gore u Švjetskoj našoj emisiji,

1102
00:48:36,620 --> 00:48:39,940
 rekao je, prvo sam krenuo sa tim susretima za mlade,

1103
00:48:40,860 --> 00:48:42,940
 i vidim, ajde, napredu je dobro,

1104
00:48:42,940 --> 00:48:45,040
 ide godinu dana, je to išlo.

1105
00:48:45,040 --> 00:48:46,460
 I nakon toga se,

1106
00:48:46,460 --> 00:48:48,440
 kroz to vrijeme se formira ovih zbor.

1107
00:48:48,440 --> 00:48:51,840
 Ali vidio sam i ovi plus 40,

1108
00:48:51,840 --> 00:48:53,140
 imamo dvije grupe,

1109
00:48:53,140 --> 00:48:54,900
 to 40 i plus 40,

1110
00:48:54,900 --> 00:48:56,560
 rekao, i njima treba.

1111
00:48:56,560 --> 00:48:57,660
 I oni su žedni.

1112
00:48:57,660 --> 00:48:59,840
 I onda, kako ćemo, šta ćemo,

1113
00:48:59,840 --> 00:49:01,800
 oje FES, Frama,

1114
00:49:01,800 --> 00:49:04,620
 ne može, Frama, ovi su u godinama.

1115
00:49:04,620 --> 00:49:06,560
 I onda, ajmo mi jednu molitvenu zajednicu.

1116
00:49:06,560 --> 00:49:08,320
 Onda sam otišao od Zagreb

1117
00:49:08,320 --> 00:49:09,720
 i sjećam se gore u

1118
00:49:09,720 --> 00:49:12,020
 ovaj Hrvatskom institutu

1119
00:49:12,020 --> 00:49:13,280
 za liturgijski pastoral.

1120
00:49:13,280 --> 00:49:15,980
 Ja govorim, žena, daj mi 90 časoslova.

1121
00:49:15,980 --> 00:49:18,020
 Jer nekako sam dugo razmatrao,

1122
00:49:18,020 --> 00:49:19,540
 bože, evo, šta ću, kako ću.

1123
00:49:19,540 --> 00:49:21,020
 I rekao, ide mi,

1124
00:49:21,020 --> 00:49:23,220
 ja ću njih naučiti molitve crkve.

1125
00:49:23,220 --> 00:49:25,760
 Časoslovi, božanski časoslov,

1126
00:49:25,760 --> 00:49:27,280
 liturgija časova,

1127
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:28,920
 i zaista se to lijepo prihvatili.

1128
00:49:28,920 --> 00:49:30,960
 Kaže, žena, gdje ide u časoslovi,

1129
00:49:30,960 --> 00:49:32,800
 ova prodavačica, ja govorim u šitavsku.

1130
00:49:32,800 --> 00:49:34,180
 Kaže, pa si kad vam čuli za to.

1131
00:49:34,180 --> 00:49:36,340
 Rekao, nisu, ali sad će čuti.

1132
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:39,440
 Tako da, ovaj, evo, to je jedna jako lijepa

1133
00:49:39,440 --> 00:49:42,000
 molitva crkve, u kojoj zaista, evo,

1134
00:49:42,000 --> 00:49:44,880
 sudjeluje cijelo tijelo crkve,

1135
00:49:44,880 --> 00:49:46,480
 kada se, kada molimo, evo,

1136
00:49:46,480 --> 00:49:48,820
 božanski časoslov, ti isto to dobro znaš,

1137
00:49:48,820 --> 00:49:50,680
 evo, tu si u EFES-u,

1138
00:49:50,680 --> 00:49:53,320
 član si, tako da znaš kako je da ta molitva.

1139
00:49:54,180 --> 00:49:55,540
 I, evo, Bogu hvala,

1140
00:49:55,540 --> 00:49:57,080
 da se od napredu ide dobro,

1141
00:49:57,080 --> 00:49:58,540
 ali idemo korak po korak,

1142
00:49:58,540 --> 00:49:59,480
 ne treba žuriti,

1143
00:49:59,480 --> 00:50:01,180
 pa evo, vidit ćemo,

1144
00:50:01,180 --> 00:50:02,680
 gdje će me gospodin dalje odvesti,

1145
00:50:02,680 --> 00:50:04,020
 koliko će se tu zadržati,

1146
00:50:04,020 --> 00:50:05,500
 hoće li promijeniti misiju,

1147
00:50:05,500 --> 00:50:06,820
 hoće li se vratiti nazad,

1148
00:50:06,820 --> 00:50:08,500
 u Božije ruke, evo,

1149
00:50:08,500 --> 00:50:10,160
 ko što i sada sam otišao gore,

1150
00:50:10,160 --> 00:50:11,820
 u Božijom provjednošću,

1151
00:50:11,820 --> 00:50:14,660
 tek sam nakon nekog vremena

1152
00:50:14,660 --> 00:50:15,920
 shvatio svoj smisao,

1153
00:50:15,920 --> 00:50:16,840
 zašto sam gore,

1154
00:50:16,840 --> 00:50:18,360
 u početku, naravno,

1155
00:50:18,360 --> 00:50:19,860
 ideš u nepoznato,

1156
00:50:19,860 --> 00:50:22,140
 tako će gospodin provjediti zadalje,

1157
00:50:22,140 --> 00:50:23,660
 evo, gdje god bude njegova volja,

1158
00:50:23,660 --> 00:50:25,400
 tu smo najbolji,

1159
00:50:25,400 --> 00:50:26,200
 tu će biti najbolji,

1160
00:50:26,200 --> 00:50:27,280
 tu će biti najsigurniji,

1161
00:50:27,280 --> 00:50:29,640
 evo, on nas neće sigurno ostaviti.

1162
00:50:29,640 --> 00:50:32,460
 I, upravo, spomenuo Međugorje i Mladifest,

1163
00:50:32,460 --> 00:50:33,620
 mi, evo, snimamo vrijeme,

1164
00:50:33,620 --> 00:50:34,720
 Mladifest,

1165
00:50:34,720 --> 00:50:35,720
 a, upravo, je nekako,

1166
00:50:35,720 --> 00:50:38,160
 Međugorje pokazate koliko je,

1167
00:50:38,160 --> 00:50:41,280
 koliko vani vlada ta neka pustor,

1168
00:50:41,280 --> 00:50:42,160
 kad vidimo, evo,

1169
00:50:42,160 --> 00:50:44,140
 štine dajove godine,

1170
00:50:44,400 --> 00:50:47,060
 70 i neka, nešto, zemalja bilo,

1171
00:50:47,060 --> 00:50:48,080
 ono, kad vidiš da ljudi

1172
00:50:48,080 --> 00:50:50,040
 iz Koreje, iz Kine,

1173
00:50:50,040 --> 00:50:51,980
 iz nekih afričkih zemalja,

1174
00:50:51,980 --> 00:50:52,720
 ne znam, no, dakle,

1175
00:50:52,720 --> 00:50:55,240
 sve ljudi ne dolaze ovdje u Međugorje,

1176
00:50:55,240 --> 00:50:56,660
 ono, baš neki pokazate.

1177
00:50:56,660 --> 00:50:58,640
 Tako je, tako je,

1178
00:50:58,640 --> 00:51:00,700
 ovdje je zaista velika milost,

1179
00:51:00,700 --> 00:51:01,920
 velika milost,

1180
00:51:01,920 --> 00:51:02,480
 ja znam,

1181
00:51:02,480 --> 00:51:03,840
 zase, po sebi,

1182
00:51:03,840 --> 00:51:06,300
 tek u svom obraćenju,

1183
00:51:06,300 --> 00:51:07,640
 tamo nekak kad sam malo,

1184
00:51:07,640 --> 00:51:09,160
 jedno, dublje u životni put,

1185
00:51:09,160 --> 00:51:10,860
 išao sam ja u crku i sve,

1186
00:51:10,860 --> 00:51:12,880
 ali, zaista je to bilo jedno obraćenje,

1187
00:51:13,560 --> 00:51:14,300
 jer ljudi misle,

1188
00:51:14,300 --> 00:51:15,800
 obraćenje mora biti nešto veliko,

1189
00:51:15,800 --> 00:51:17,900
 sve ti pao, ono, pao s konja,

1190
00:51:17,900 --> 00:51:19,140
 ovaj,

1191
00:51:19,140 --> 00:51:20,900
 ne mora to biti veliko,

1192
00:51:20,900 --> 00:51:22,860
 veliko je uvijek u Božijim očima,

1193
00:51:22,860 --> 00:51:24,180
 svako obraćenje je veliko,

1194
00:51:24,180 --> 00:51:25,560
 ovaj,

1195
00:51:25,560 --> 00:51:27,500
 tek tada shvatiš,

1196
00:51:27,500 --> 00:51:28,820
 ja sam zapravo,

1197
00:51:28,820 --> 00:51:29,780
 tek s 18 godina,

1198
00:51:29,780 --> 00:51:30,580
 još živio sam ovdje,

1199
00:51:30,580 --> 00:51:32,300
 s 18 godina sam,

1200
00:51:32,300 --> 00:51:34,700
 ajmo re, saznao, spoznao,

1201
00:51:34,700 --> 00:51:35,760
 počelo me zanimati,

1202
00:51:35,760 --> 00:51:37,340
 da se Gospod kazala u Međugorju,

1203
00:51:37,580 --> 00:51:38,460
 čuva sam ja možda to,

1204
00:51:38,460 --> 00:51:39,000
 ali, ono,

1205
00:51:39,000 --> 00:51:39,660
 to mi je bilo,

1206
00:51:39,660 --> 00:51:40,980
 okej, super, šta sad,

1207
00:51:40,980 --> 00:51:41,960
 tako da,

1208
00:51:41,960 --> 00:51:43,920
 vjerujem da i ovdje dosta ljudi,

1209
00:51:43,920 --> 00:51:45,700
 nesreća tu milost Međugorja,

1210
00:51:45,700 --> 00:51:47,080
 to je,

1211
00:51:47,080 --> 00:51:49,460
 kako nas je Gospod i nebo nagradilo,

1212
00:51:49,460 --> 00:51:50,880
 pa mi nismo svjesni,

1213
00:51:50,880 --> 00:51:52,860
 mi nismo svjesni,

1214
00:51:54,140 --> 00:51:55,140
 i zato mi je žao,

1215
00:51:55,140 --> 00:51:55,600
 ono,

1216
00:51:55,600 --> 00:51:56,780
 kad si tu,

1217
00:51:56,780 --> 00:51:57,520
 imaš milost,

1218
00:51:57,520 --> 00:51:59,000
 evo, ja sam Bogu hvala radovito,

1219
00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:00,200
 i dok sam bilo na širokom brijegu,

1220
00:52:00,200 --> 00:52:01,040
 odlazi u Međugorje,

1221
00:52:01,040 --> 00:52:01,340
 jer je ono,

1222
00:52:01,340 --> 00:52:03,220
 značajno za moj osobni,

1223
00:52:03,220 --> 00:52:04,060
 ovaj,

1224
00:52:04,060 --> 00:52:04,520
 put,

1225
00:52:04,520 --> 00:52:05,620
 gospodinu,

1226
00:52:05,620 --> 00:52:06,160
 pa,

1227
00:52:06,160 --> 00:52:07,700
 zato mi je bilo,

1228
00:52:07,700 --> 00:52:08,940
 i dok sam bio tu,

1229
00:52:08,940 --> 00:52:09,840
 jako važno,

1230
00:52:09,840 --> 00:52:10,200
 otići,

1231
00:52:10,200 --> 00:52:11,320
 biti prisutan tamo,

1232
00:52:11,320 --> 00:52:12,500
 s majkom,

1233
00:52:12,500 --> 00:52:13,500
 ali,

1234
00:52:13,500 --> 00:52:15,140
 posebno,

1235
00:52:15,140 --> 00:52:15,860
 kad odeš vani,

1236
00:52:15,860 --> 00:52:16,640
 onda vidiš,

1237
00:52:16,640 --> 00:52:17,540
 okej,

1238
00:52:17,540 --> 00:52:19,820
 zato toliko ljudi dolazi,

1239
00:52:19,820 --> 00:52:21,720
 puno ti je jasnija slika,

1240
00:52:22,100 --> 00:52:23,960
 što ti kažeš preko 70 zemalja,

1241
00:52:23,960 --> 00:52:25,440
 i svi koji jedno,

1242
00:52:25,440 --> 00:52:27,080
 pa to je čudesno,

1243
00:52:27,080 --> 00:52:27,760
 to je preljepo,

1244
00:52:27,760 --> 00:52:28,560
 to ne znam,

1245
00:52:28,560 --> 00:52:29,000
 evo,

1246
00:52:29,000 --> 00:52:30,200
 osim na svjetskom susretu,

1247
00:52:30,200 --> 00:52:30,660
 mladi,

1248
00:52:30,660 --> 00:52:32,240
 da ima i gdje drugo u svijetu,

1249
00:52:32,240 --> 00:52:33,420
 da se tako okupi,

1250
00:52:33,420 --> 00:52:34,840
 i stoliko zemalja,

1251
00:52:34,840 --> 00:52:35,940
 i da svi dišu koji jedno,

1252
00:52:35,940 --> 00:52:37,740
 zato što u Kristu smo svi jedno,

1253
00:52:37,740 --> 00:52:38,860
 kaže Pavel,

1254
00:52:38,860 --> 00:52:40,380
 nema više židovog grk,

1255
00:52:40,380 --> 00:52:41,580
 rob slobodnjak,

1256
00:52:41,580 --> 00:52:43,080
 svi smo jedno u gospodinu,

1257
00:52:43,080 --> 00:52:44,340
 i kad to shvatimo,

1258
00:52:44,340 --> 00:52:45,220
 zato ja uvijek,

1259
00:52:45,220 --> 00:52:49,360
 sa tugom nekako govorim,

1260
00:52:50,500 --> 00:52:51,580
 o švicarcima,

1261
00:52:51,580 --> 00:52:54,200
 i navješta našim ljudima,

1262
00:52:54,200 --> 00:52:56,240
 ne to hrvaststvo,

1263
00:52:56,240 --> 00:52:57,220
 ne nacionalizam,

1264
00:52:57,220 --> 00:52:58,420
 koji nije toliko važan,

1265
00:52:58,420 --> 00:52:59,060
 nego,

1266
00:52:59,060 --> 00:53:00,360
 švicaraci,

1267
00:53:00,360 --> 00:53:00,960
 Njemaci,

1268
00:53:00,960 --> 00:53:01,440
 Portugali,

1269
00:53:01,440 --> 00:53:02,240
 šta god da si,

1270
00:53:02,240 --> 00:53:04,000
 želiš služi Kristu,

1271
00:53:04,000 --> 00:53:04,940
 idemo,

1272
00:53:04,940 --> 00:53:06,480
 idemo zajedno,

1273
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:07,360
 znači,

1274
00:53:07,360 --> 00:53:07,900
 vjera,

1275
00:53:07,900 --> 00:53:09,180
 iznad nacije,

1276
00:53:09,180 --> 00:53:10,500
 iznad naše narodnosti,

1277
00:53:10,500 --> 00:53:11,860
 i to je jako važno,

1278
00:53:11,940 --> 00:53:14,120
 zato mi je drago,

1279
00:53:14,120 --> 00:53:15,140
 govor je uvijek sustresti,

1280
00:53:15,140 --> 00:53:16,520
 i švicarce,

1281
00:53:16,520 --> 00:53:17,260
 koji su pobožni,

1282
00:53:17,260 --> 00:53:18,200
 koji mole krunicu,

1283
00:53:18,200 --> 00:53:19,100
 koji idu u crkvu,

1284
00:53:19,100 --> 00:53:19,760
 evo,

1285
00:53:19,760 --> 00:53:20,600
 nedavno smo imali,

1286
00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:22,860
 u San Galenu je dolazio,

1287
00:53:22,860 --> 00:53:23,780
 ovaj,

1288
00:53:23,780 --> 00:53:24,700
 iz Međugorja,

1289
00:53:24,700 --> 00:53:25,840
 Ivan Vidijoc,

1290
00:53:25,840 --> 00:53:27,060
 i upravo,

1291
00:53:27,060 --> 00:53:27,320
 evo,

1292
00:53:27,320 --> 00:53:27,800
 taj dan,

1293
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:29,440
 on ima i dalje gospina ukazanja,

1294
00:53:29,440 --> 00:53:31,040
 bilo je ukazanje u crkvi,

1295
00:53:31,040 --> 00:53:31,760
 to je upravo,

1296
00:53:31,760 --> 00:53:33,500
 švicarci su organizirali,

1297
00:53:33,500 --> 00:53:35,820
 Marija Švajc se zove,

1298
00:53:36,240 --> 00:53:37,200
 organizacija odruga,

1299
00:53:37,200 --> 00:53:39,840
 i došlo je puno Hrvata,

1300
00:53:39,840 --> 00:53:41,040
 puna je crkva bila,

1301
00:53:41,040 --> 00:53:43,240
 i moje prvo iskustvo,

1302
00:53:43,240 --> 00:53:44,680
 da sam bio baš,

1303
00:53:44,680 --> 00:53:44,940
 ono,

1304
00:53:44,940 --> 00:53:45,860
 na ukazanju,

1305
00:53:45,860 --> 00:53:46,940
 tik uz Ivana,

1306
00:53:46,940 --> 00:53:48,660
 i bilo je predivno,

1307
00:53:48,660 --> 00:53:49,340
 zaista,

1308
00:53:49,340 --> 00:53:49,840
 ono,

1309
00:53:49,840 --> 00:53:51,980
 moja vjera u Međugorje je toliko snažna,

1310
00:53:51,980 --> 00:53:52,380
 ja znam,

1311
00:53:52,380 --> 00:53:54,860
 mi nismo dužni vjerovati u Međugorje,

1312
00:53:54,860 --> 00:53:56,480
 to nije nikakva dogma,

1313
00:53:56,480 --> 00:53:57,660
 ovaj,

1314
00:53:57,660 --> 00:53:58,100
 to je,

1315
00:53:58,100 --> 00:53:59,960
 osobno ukazanje,

1316
00:53:59,960 --> 00:54:01,160
 koje se dogodilo vidiocima,

1317
00:54:01,160 --> 00:54:02,700
 ali ljudi moji,

1318
00:54:02,700 --> 00:54:04,500
 pa pogledajte plodove,

1319
00:54:04,500 --> 00:54:05,180
 evo ja prvi,

1320
00:54:06,020 --> 00:54:08,040
 mogu svoje duhovni put,

1321
00:54:08,040 --> 00:54:08,960
 duhovno zvanje,

1322
00:54:08,960 --> 00:54:09,720
 zasigurno,

1323
00:54:09,720 --> 00:54:11,000
 između ostalog,

1324
00:54:11,000 --> 00:54:11,500
 zahvaliti,

1325
00:54:11,500 --> 00:54:12,360
 a možda najviše,

1326
00:54:12,360 --> 00:54:13,080
 zapravo,

1327
00:54:13,080 --> 00:54:13,740
 u Međugorju,

1328
00:54:13,740 --> 00:54:16,500
 i tu je rijeka milosti,

1329
00:54:16,500 --> 00:54:17,580
 rijeka milosti,

1330
00:54:17,580 --> 00:54:19,140
 ne treba i nama nikakvi znakovi,

1331
00:54:19,140 --> 00:54:20,480
 nikakva čudesa,

1332
00:54:20,480 --> 00:54:23,100
 dovoljno je da vidimo koliko se ljudi obraćaju,

1333
00:54:23,100 --> 00:54:24,560
 to je sasvim dovoljno,

1334
00:54:24,560 --> 00:54:25,620
 a meni kad me pita,

1335
00:54:25,620 --> 00:54:25,960
 i tako,

1336
00:54:25,960 --> 00:54:28,060
 ja ne vjerujem u Međugorje,

1337
00:54:28,060 --> 00:54:29,480
 pa ne moraš ne vjerovati,

1338
00:54:29,480 --> 00:54:30,760
 ja kažem,

1339
00:54:30,760 --> 00:54:31,480
 ja vjerujem,

1340
00:54:31,480 --> 00:54:33,440
 ali isto tako,

1341
00:54:34,100 --> 00:54:35,240
 neću nikak ovjeravati,

1342
00:54:35,240 --> 00:54:36,160
 ja znam,

1343
00:54:36,160 --> 00:54:36,620
 ja mogu,

1344
00:54:36,620 --> 00:54:37,480
 ako me pitaš,

1345
00:54:37,480 --> 00:54:38,560
 ja ću svoj vlasti put,

1346
00:54:38,560 --> 00:54:40,360
 svoj vlasti doživljaju Međugorja,

1347
00:54:40,360 --> 00:54:43,420
 vjerujem da ljude nisu iskusili milost Međugorja,

1348
00:54:43,420 --> 00:54:45,040
 pa možda zato tako govore,

1349
00:54:45,040 --> 00:54:46,980
 ali po mene najveći dokaz,

1350
00:54:46,980 --> 00:54:50,380
 da se gospa zaista ukazala,

1351
00:54:50,380 --> 00:54:52,480
 osim ovih obraćenja koje se događaju,

1352
00:54:52,780 --> 00:54:54,720
 jer kaže Isus po plodovima ćete i preposnati,

1353
00:54:54,720 --> 00:54:57,160
 zamislite vi djecu,

1354
00:54:57,160 --> 00:54:59,800
 može li djete nešto slagati,

1355
00:54:59,800 --> 00:55:00,760
 šutiti,

1356
00:55:00,760 --> 00:55:01,900
 ne znam,

1357
00:55:01,900 --> 00:55:02,960
 pet minuta,

1358
00:55:02,960 --> 00:55:03,800
 jedan dan,

1359
00:55:03,800 --> 00:55:05,220
 kamo je toliko godina,

1360
00:55:05,220 --> 00:55:06,260
 djeca,

1361
00:55:06,260 --> 00:55:07,080
 mučena,

1362
00:55:07,080 --> 00:55:08,460
 odvođena,

1363
00:55:08,460 --> 00:55:09,580
 prepadnuta,

1364
00:55:09,580 --> 00:55:10,640
 i sad,

1365
00:55:10,640 --> 00:55:11,660
 ono,

1366
00:55:11,660 --> 00:55:12,400
 sve,

1367
00:55:12,400 --> 00:55:14,260
 ubiće ih ako ne kažu,

1368
00:55:14,260 --> 00:55:15,960
 da se gospa nije ukazala,

1369
00:55:15,960 --> 00:55:16,620
 ali ne,

1370
00:55:16,620 --> 00:55:17,600
 one drže svoje,

1371
00:55:17,920 --> 00:55:19,020
 nismo vidjeli gospu,

1372
00:55:19,020 --> 00:55:21,240
 nismo vidjeli gospu,

1373
00:55:21,240 --> 00:55:22,840
 i to je nešto predivno,

1374
00:55:22,840 --> 00:55:26,240
 i daj Bože da postanemo,

1375
00:55:26,240 --> 00:55:27,700
 vjerujem da smo svjesni,

1376
00:55:27,700 --> 00:55:30,520
 ali još više svjesni dara,

1377
00:55:30,520 --> 00:55:32,100
 evo koji nam je nebo ovdje dalo,

1378
00:55:32,100 --> 00:55:33,320
 naša međuporba,

1379
00:55:33,320 --> 00:55:33,780
 zaista,

1380
00:55:33,780 --> 00:55:35,520
 bio sam i u drugim svetištima,

1381
00:55:35,520 --> 00:55:36,600
 u,

1382
00:55:36,600 --> 00:55:37,640
 po svijetu,

1383
00:55:37,640 --> 00:55:39,100
 gospodnim svetištima,

1384
00:55:39,100 --> 00:55:41,460
 inače kažu uvijek je,

1385
00:55:41,460 --> 00:55:42,100
 ono,

1386
00:55:42,100 --> 00:55:43,520
 kući kad je tu blizu,

1387
00:55:43,520 --> 00:55:43,860
 ono,

1388
00:55:43,860 --> 00:55:45,920
 ajde uzmiješ nekako zdravo za gotovo,

1389
00:55:45,920 --> 00:55:47,900
 ljepše uvijek nekako drugdje vanje,

1390
00:55:47,920 --> 00:55:50,220
 ali meni je iskreno najljepše u Međugorje,

1391
00:55:50,220 --> 00:55:52,040
 cvije gospodini svetištima u kojima sam bio,

1392
00:55:52,040 --> 00:55:53,240
 ovaj,

1393
00:55:53,240 --> 00:55:54,680
 Međugorje mi je posebno,

1394
00:55:54,680 --> 00:55:56,620
 je li to zato što tu još,

1395
00:55:56,620 --> 00:55:57,760
 to sve živi,

1396
00:55:57,760 --> 00:55:59,560
 što ukazanje još nisu prestala,

1397
00:55:59,560 --> 00:56:00,560
 moguće,

1398
00:56:00,560 --> 00:56:02,000
 ali evo,

1399
00:56:02,000 --> 00:56:03,440
 u Božje ruke,

1400
00:56:03,440 --> 00:56:05,000
 gospodinu se nijedne žuri,

1401
00:56:05,000 --> 00:56:07,000
 ako gledamo sprem vječnosti,

1402
00:56:07,000 --> 00:56:08,480
 život nema kraja,

1403
00:56:08,480 --> 00:56:09,780
 nema vremena,

1404
00:56:09,780 --> 00:56:10,780
 nema dana,

1405
00:56:10,780 --> 00:56:11,920
 nema sati,

1406
00:56:11,920 --> 00:56:13,960
 tako da gospodin ide polako,

1407
00:56:13,960 --> 00:56:16,720
 njemu je najvažnije da se čovjek obrati,

1408
00:56:16,720 --> 00:56:18,000
 prije svoje smrti,

1409
00:56:18,000 --> 00:56:19,520
 i na to smo pozvani,

1410
00:56:19,520 --> 00:56:21,020
 tako da polako,

1411
00:56:21,020 --> 00:56:22,700
 pozivati na obraćanje,

1412
00:56:22,700 --> 00:56:24,300
 ali nikoga ne siliti,

1413
00:56:24,300 --> 00:56:26,400
 tako i gospodin uvijek mirno,

1414
00:56:26,400 --> 00:56:27,840
 poruka dođe,

1415
00:56:27,840 --> 00:56:29,020
 koje prečita,

1416
00:56:29,020 --> 00:56:29,440
 vidi,

1417
00:56:29,440 --> 00:56:30,180
 živi,

1418
00:56:30,180 --> 00:56:31,020
 lijepo,

1419
00:56:31,020 --> 00:56:32,240
 a za ostale,

1420
00:56:32,240 --> 00:56:34,260
 nadamo se da će i oni prihvatiti tu poruku.

1421
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:35,920
 Sad si to malo spomenuo,

1422
00:56:35,920 --> 00:56:37,800
 svoj osobni put,

1423
00:56:37,800 --> 00:56:39,700
 i poze,

1424
00:56:39,700 --> 00:56:42,440
 o kako je izgledao taj tvoj duhovni put,

1425
00:56:42,440 --> 00:56:42,900
 poze,

1426
00:56:42,900 --> 00:56:43,720
 zaradovništvo,

1427
00:56:43,720 --> 00:56:44,540
 svećeništvo,

1428
00:56:44,540 --> 00:56:44,920
 obraćenje.

1429
00:56:44,920 --> 00:56:46,100
 Duhovni put,

1430
00:56:46,100 --> 00:56:47,160
 obraćenje,

1431
00:56:47,160 --> 00:56:48,460
 evo ovako,

1432
00:56:48,460 --> 00:56:49,500
 pokušat ćemo,

1433
00:56:49,500 --> 00:56:51,560
 ukratko to sažeti.

1434
00:56:51,560 --> 00:56:52,680
 A ništa ukratko,

1435
00:56:52,680 --> 00:56:53,460
 pričaj ti.

1436
00:56:53,460 --> 00:56:55,120
 Ti si već slušao,

1437
00:56:55,120 --> 00:56:55,540
 ovaj,

1438
00:56:55,540 --> 00:56:55,860
 to,

1439
00:56:55,860 --> 00:56:56,340
 mislim,

1440
00:56:56,340 --> 00:56:57,100
 par puta,

1441
00:56:57,100 --> 00:56:57,500
 čak,

1442
00:56:57,500 --> 00:56:59,180
 imao sam svjedočanstva,

1443
00:56:59,180 --> 00:57:00,280
 na nekim seminarima,

1444
00:57:00,280 --> 00:57:00,620
 ili tako,

1445
00:57:00,620 --> 00:57:01,840
 za manje grupe ljudi,

1446
00:57:02,520 --> 00:57:03,900
 čak imao svjedočanstvo

1447
00:57:03,900 --> 00:57:06,920
 i činim se 2015. godine u Zagrebu,

1448
00:57:06,920 --> 00:57:08,600
 kad sam gore bio student,

1449
00:57:08,600 --> 00:57:12,060
 onda smo snimali ovu spot za pjesmu Hvala Radovnika

1450
00:57:12,060 --> 00:57:13,600
 i sad na promociji tog spota

1451
00:57:13,600 --> 00:57:15,280
 je trebao neko svjedočiti,

1452
00:57:15,280 --> 00:57:17,360
 moj brat Ivan Dominik Ilčić,

1453
00:57:17,360 --> 00:57:18,740
 tada je rekao,

1454
00:57:18,740 --> 00:57:18,960
 ajde,

1455
00:57:18,960 --> 00:57:19,660
 mogo si ti,

1456
00:57:19,660 --> 00:57:20,300
 mogo si,

1457
00:57:20,300 --> 00:57:21,000
 ajde,

1458
00:57:21,000 --> 00:57:21,900
 dobro hoću i,

1459
00:57:21,900 --> 00:57:24,480
 evo ima taj snimak i sada,

1460
00:57:24,480 --> 00:57:26,420
 na društvenim mrežama,

1461
00:57:26,420 --> 00:57:26,540
 na YouTube.

1462
00:57:26,540 --> 00:57:28,200
 A ti pričao je ovdje da ljudi ne traže.

1463
00:57:28,200 --> 00:57:28,600
 Dobro,

1464
00:57:28,600 --> 00:57:28,960
 dobro,

1465
00:57:28,960 --> 00:57:30,240
 da ljudi ne traže,

1466
00:57:30,240 --> 00:57:32,580
 ja ću malo sa probati to nekako skratno

1467
00:57:32,580 --> 00:57:33,840
 i ću baš previše širiti.

1468
00:57:33,840 --> 00:57:35,960
 Duhovni poziv.

1469
00:57:35,960 --> 00:57:37,060
 Evo,

1470
00:57:37,060 --> 00:57:40,640
 rekao bih da je naš duhovni put svakog čovjeka

1471
00:57:40,640 --> 00:57:43,980
 put koji traje do naše smrti.

1472
00:57:43,980 --> 00:57:45,040
 Tako da,

1473
00:57:45,040 --> 00:57:48,260
 nismo nikad dovoljno formiran,

1474
00:57:48,260 --> 00:57:49,340
 nikad dovoljno oblikovani.

1475
00:57:49,340 --> 00:57:51,980
 Zato se ljudi progrešava i svetim tek nakon smrti.

1476
00:57:51,980 --> 00:57:53,700
 Jer ti možeš živjeti sveto

1477
00:57:53,700 --> 00:57:55,240
 do pred kraja života

1478
00:57:55,240 --> 00:57:57,100
 i onda napraviš neki problem šta sad.

1479
00:57:57,100 --> 00:57:59,500
 Naravno, Bogu hvala ima sveta ispovijed.

1480
00:58:00,020 --> 00:58:00,720
 Tako da, evo,

1481
00:58:00,720 --> 00:58:01,780
 može se riješi grijeha,

1482
00:58:01,780 --> 00:58:03,180
 ali nikad ne znaš.

1483
00:58:03,180 --> 00:58:04,820
 Tako da, uvijek je to jedna borba.

1484
00:58:04,820 --> 00:58:08,420
 Ali, evo, što se tiče mog osobnog duhovnog puta,

1485
00:58:08,420 --> 00:58:10,760
 pa ja sam ti

1486
00:58:10,760 --> 00:58:12,660
 kao, evo,

1487
00:58:12,660 --> 00:58:15,540
 odgojen u kršćanskoj katoličkoj obitelji

1488
00:58:15,540 --> 00:58:17,060
 i išao sam, evo,

1489
00:58:17,060 --> 00:58:18,620
 radovito medaljem na svetu misu.

1490
00:58:18,620 --> 00:58:20,060
 Tako sam i naučen

1491
00:58:20,060 --> 00:58:21,700
 i to je sve bilo super.

1492
00:58:21,700 --> 00:58:22,640
 Tako da, evo,

1493
00:58:22,640 --> 00:58:24,840
 to je neko moje osnovno školsko razdoblje.

1494
00:58:26,240 --> 00:58:30,580
 Peo sam u jednom i tječenem zboru koji je tada bio aktualan u jednoj župi,

1495
00:58:30,580 --> 00:58:34,580
 ali nekako nisam nikad dublje proniknuo u tu vjeru.

1496
00:58:34,580 --> 00:58:37,280
 To je bila nedeljna misa jer je to bilo obaveza,

1497
00:58:37,280 --> 00:58:40,100
 ali neke dubine tu nije bilo.

1498
00:58:41,100 --> 00:58:45,000
 I zapravo moj pravi duhovni put

1499
00:58:45,000 --> 00:58:49,480
 rekao bi da kreće tek tamo od 18. godine

1500
00:58:49,480 --> 00:58:52,560
 kada sam upisao fakultet, evo, u Mostaru.

1501
00:58:52,560 --> 00:58:55,940
 Inače, ako ne znate, prazlasko imalo dvola završena fakulteta.

1502
00:58:55,940 --> 00:58:57,320
 Teologija i?

1503
00:58:57,320 --> 00:58:59,680
 Teologija i agronomija u Mostaru.

1504
00:58:59,680 --> 00:59:03,900
 Dobar, to je, nije toliko bitna informacija,

1505
00:59:03,900 --> 00:59:05,960
 ali evo, da se mi vratimo na ovu priču.

1506
00:59:05,960 --> 00:59:08,480
 I što se tiče srednje škole, evo,

1507
00:59:08,480 --> 00:59:10,940
 tu ću malo neke stvari samo naglasiti.

1508
00:59:11,100 --> 00:59:15,240
 Kako je gledal moj odlazak nedeljni na misu?

1509
00:59:15,240 --> 00:59:18,520
 Evo, imali ste već eno sredočanstvo

1510
00:59:18,520 --> 00:59:21,980
 o poteškoćama i kocke.

1511
00:59:21,980 --> 00:59:26,080
 Mislim da je tata od našeg fraželjka bio u emisiji.

1512
00:59:26,080 --> 00:59:30,180
 I evo, ja nisam bio zaglibio sad nešto toliko u kocku,

1513
00:59:30,180 --> 00:59:34,580
 ali koliko mogu reći zapravo da nisam bio zaglibio u kladionicu,

1514
00:59:34,580 --> 00:59:36,660
 ako sam bio u njoj svaki dan.

1515
00:59:36,660 --> 00:59:39,920
 Pa čak možda onda mogu reći da sam zaglibio.

1516
00:59:40,340 --> 00:59:43,880
 Ali s druge strane, nisam zaglibio što se tiče nekih dugova,

1517
00:59:43,880 --> 00:59:46,880
 što se tiče nekih velikih ulaganja

1518
00:59:46,880 --> 00:59:49,960
 u nešto što nema nikakvu budućnost.

1519
00:59:49,960 --> 00:59:52,300
 Ali jednostavno, bio si okružen,

1520
00:59:52,300 --> 00:59:54,980
 zato evo, jako važno, to je poruka roditeljima,

1521
00:59:56,420 --> 00:59:58,100
 provjeravajte s kim se vaša djeca druže,

1522
00:59:58,100 --> 00:59:59,960
 vodite svoju djecu u crkvu što češće,

1523
00:59:59,960 --> 01:00:02,960
 da se uključe u zbor, da se uključe u ministrante,

1524
01:00:02,960 --> 01:00:05,960
 da se uključe u bilo kakvu crkvenu organizaciju.

1525
01:00:07,440 --> 01:00:09,420
 Jer ako tebe odgaja društvo,

1526
01:00:09,420 --> 01:00:11,840
 a sve nas odgaja društvo u srednjoj školi,

1527
01:00:11,840 --> 01:00:15,580
 onda ti upaneš u neke teške probleme.

1528
01:00:16,320 --> 01:00:19,720
 Evo, rećemo, to ću istaknuti,

1529
01:00:19,720 --> 01:00:23,320
 jer je jedna jako važna stvar za moje obraćanje bila.

1530
01:00:23,320 --> 01:00:27,480
 Kroz srednju školu, kažem, bio sam u društvu

1531
01:00:27,480 --> 01:00:30,020
 koje je promicalo sve one stvari

1532
01:00:30,020 --> 01:00:31,780
 koje nisu dobre, vrednote.

1533
01:00:31,780 --> 01:00:37,140
 Naravno, to je odnosi prije braka,

1534
01:00:37,140 --> 01:00:40,140
 koje su, naravno, tek kaznje je shvatio

1535
01:00:40,140 --> 01:00:42,100
 Bogu hvala, nisam ih ne imao,

1536
01:00:42,100 --> 01:00:44,540
 ali, kažem, bio si u takvom društvu

1537
01:00:44,540 --> 01:00:45,860
 gdje si bio pre blizu toga.

1538
01:00:46,320 --> 01:00:47,440
 gdje je to bilo normalno.

1539
01:00:47,440 --> 01:00:51,280
 I sada, ti živiš u takvom društvu,

1540
01:00:51,280 --> 01:00:53,060
 ako nisi u tome,

1541
01:00:53,060 --> 01:00:54,500
 onda nije dobro.

1542
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:56,280
 Ne možeš biti dio toga društva.

1543
01:00:56,280 --> 01:00:58,720
 I naravno se čovjek boji da ne ostane sam.

1544
01:00:58,720 --> 01:01:01,200
 A ako vidiš da još ima takvih ljudi

1545
01:01:01,200 --> 01:01:02,640
 koji želi živjeti evanđijoski,

1546
01:01:02,640 --> 01:01:04,960
 da ima drugi način, da ima bolje nešto,

1547
01:01:04,960 --> 01:01:06,580
 ako imaš više ponuda,

1548
01:01:06,580 --> 01:01:08,400
 onda vidiš, ej, nisam sam,

1549
01:01:08,400 --> 01:01:10,880
 ima još oni koji su, što ovi kažu,

1550
01:01:10,880 --> 01:01:11,940
 mi nisam normalni.

1551
01:01:11,940 --> 01:01:13,840
 Gdje se ne spava prije braka.

1552
01:01:14,560 --> 01:01:16,640
 Kako mi tu spolnost svedemo

1553
01:01:16,640 --> 01:01:19,320
 na minimalni užitak,

1554
01:01:19,320 --> 01:01:21,700
 na nešto što je toliko prolazno,

1555
01:01:21,700 --> 01:01:22,540
 što je nevažno.

1556
01:01:22,540 --> 01:01:24,560
 A Bog nam je dao dar spolnost

1557
01:01:24,560 --> 01:01:25,460
 da njemu uživamo.

1558
01:01:25,460 --> 01:01:26,800
 Ali zna se kada.

1559
01:01:26,800 --> 01:01:28,260
 Zna se kada.

1560
01:01:28,260 --> 01:01:29,880
 To isto je jedan veliki problem gore

1561
01:01:29,880 --> 01:01:30,740
 u Švitarsku,

1562
01:01:30,740 --> 01:01:32,460
 ali evo nećemo sada skakat s teme

1563
01:01:32,460 --> 01:01:32,800
 na temu,

1564
01:01:32,800 --> 01:01:33,680
 ostaćemo na ovome.

1565
01:01:34,680 --> 01:01:36,760
 Samo želim reći u kakvom sam okruženju bio

1566
01:01:36,760 --> 01:01:37,560
 odrastao.

1567
01:01:37,560 --> 01:01:39,440
 Ne krivim te ljude,

1568
01:01:39,440 --> 01:01:40,460
 naravno.

1569
01:01:40,460 --> 01:01:42,260
 Takvo je društvo,

1570
01:01:42,260 --> 01:01:43,240
 imaš svoje razredi,

1571
01:01:43,240 --> 01:01:44,400
 ideš u takav razredi,

1572
01:01:44,400 --> 01:01:45,920
 ono, promičio se takve stvari

1573
01:01:45,920 --> 01:01:48,080
 ko me nije dano,

1574
01:01:48,080 --> 01:01:49,220
 jednostavno,

1575
01:01:49,220 --> 01:01:51,420
 ne može dati drugima.

1576
01:01:51,420 --> 01:01:54,080
 I odrastao sam u Mostaru,

1577
01:01:54,080 --> 01:01:55,420
 evo, dole sam išao u srednju

1578
01:01:55,420 --> 01:01:56,620
 građevinsku školu,

1579
01:01:57,500 --> 01:01:59,560
 sve te neke stvari su bile blizu mene,

1580
01:01:59,560 --> 01:02:00,980
 koje nisu bile dobre.

1581
01:02:00,980 --> 01:02:03,680
 Evo, najviše ću istaknuti tu u kladionicu.

1582
01:02:03,680 --> 01:02:04,880
 Ja sam vam nedjeljom,

1583
01:02:04,880 --> 01:02:07,580
 uvijek naravno bio na svetoj misi,

1584
01:02:07,580 --> 01:02:08,820
 jer sam morao.

1585
01:02:08,820 --> 01:02:12,020
 I nije to bila nešto iz moje ljubavi

1586
01:02:12,020 --> 01:02:12,960
 prema juharistiji,

1587
01:02:12,960 --> 01:02:14,820
 koju danas toliko zaista osjećam.

1588
01:02:14,820 --> 01:02:16,040
 I evo, ono,

1589
01:02:16,040 --> 01:02:19,460
 ako želite recept za svetost,

1590
01:02:19,460 --> 01:02:21,440
 samo svaki dan idete na misu.

1591
01:02:21,440 --> 01:02:22,460
 Ja kažem ljudima nekad,

1592
01:02:22,460 --> 01:02:23,920
 teško mol, teško,

1593
01:02:23,920 --> 01:02:24,920
 govorim ja, ok,

1594
01:02:24,920 --> 01:02:26,040
 sve to beskoči.

1595
01:02:26,640 --> 01:02:27,600
 Ali je uharistija.

1596
01:02:27,600 --> 01:02:30,560
 O, kad bi znali veličinu toga.

1597
01:02:30,560 --> 01:02:32,080
 Kad bi znali.

1598
01:02:32,080 --> 01:02:35,820
 Kako je sve ta misa,

1599
01:02:35,820 --> 01:02:37,020
 sve ta,

1600
01:02:37,020 --> 01:02:37,720
 kako je to,

1601
01:02:37,720 --> 01:02:38,460
 već,

1602
01:02:38,460 --> 01:02:40,320
 živjeti nebo na zemlji.

1603
01:02:40,320 --> 01:02:41,520
 Evo, ne moraš čekati nebo.

1604
01:02:41,520 --> 01:02:42,980
 Evo, imaš ga čovječe tu.

1605
01:02:42,980 --> 01:02:43,900
 Svaki dan,

1606
01:02:43,900 --> 01:02:45,360
 Krist dolazi na oltar.

1607
01:02:45,360 --> 01:02:46,440
 I tebi se daruje.

1608
01:02:46,440 --> 01:02:49,460
 Evo, tada to nisam tako osvaćao.

1609
01:02:49,460 --> 01:02:52,380
 I kažem, evo, srednja škola je tako protekla.

1610
01:02:52,380 --> 01:02:54,480
 Naravno, srednja škola,

1611
01:02:54,480 --> 01:02:55,560
 ideš na fakultet,

1612
01:02:55,660 --> 01:02:56,420
 dolaze novi ljudi,

1613
01:02:56,420 --> 01:02:57,160
 nova društva.

1614
01:02:57,160 --> 01:02:59,020
 I,

1615
01:02:59,020 --> 01:03:00,040
 tkro srednju školu,

1616
01:03:00,040 --> 01:03:00,700
 cijelo vrijeme,

1617
01:03:00,700 --> 01:03:02,080
 evo, ja i sa svojim društvom,

1618
01:03:02,080 --> 01:03:02,740
 koje je bilo,

1619
01:03:02,740 --> 01:03:03,760
 kažem,

1620
01:03:03,760 --> 01:03:04,520
 iza sve te mise,

1621
01:03:04,520 --> 01:03:05,520
 u kladioncu.

1622
01:03:05,520 --> 01:03:06,740
 I sad svi je normalno.

1623
01:03:06,740 --> 01:03:08,940
 U kladioncu.

1624
01:03:09,540 --> 01:03:10,920
 i nekad si znao ono,

1625
01:03:10,920 --> 01:03:12,600
 u jednom danu i po više listića,

1626
01:03:12,600 --> 01:03:14,220
 znao sam ja dosta puta

1627
01:03:14,220 --> 01:03:16,520
 i dobiti neki novac tu.

1628
01:03:16,520 --> 01:03:17,540
 Ali evo,

1629
01:03:17,540 --> 01:03:19,400
 to je jednostavno bila moja svakodnevica.

1630
01:03:19,400 --> 01:03:20,820
 A ako je svakodnevica,

1631
01:03:20,820 --> 01:03:21,900
 znači da je ovisno,

1632
01:03:21,900 --> 01:03:22,800
 znači da je problem.

1633
01:03:22,800 --> 01:03:23,860
 Znači da je problem.

1634
01:03:24,480 --> 01:03:24,860
 Ja ne znam,

1635
01:03:24,860 --> 01:03:27,280
 sam li kao životu više od deset maraka stavio

1636
01:03:27,280 --> 01:03:28,320
 na jedan listić.

1637
01:03:28,320 --> 01:03:29,600
 Ili možda u čitav on dan

1638
01:03:29,600 --> 01:03:30,900
 deset listića po marku.

1639
01:03:30,900 --> 01:03:31,660
 Nevažno.

1640
01:03:31,660 --> 01:03:32,600
 Tako da,

1641
01:03:32,600 --> 01:03:34,160
 s te strane je to bilo dobro.

1642
01:03:34,160 --> 01:03:34,960
 Tu me, evo,

1643
01:03:34,960 --> 01:03:36,080
 gospodin izvukao,

1644
01:03:36,080 --> 01:03:37,940
 nisem to bila neka velika olaganja,

1645
01:03:37,940 --> 01:03:40,320
 ali je zasigurno bila jedna velika ovisnost,

1646
01:03:40,320 --> 01:03:42,140
 koji je i danas veliki problem.

1647
01:03:42,140 --> 01:03:43,120
 Pogotovo u Mostaru,

1648
01:03:43,120 --> 01:03:44,480
 znači da sam odšao u postlaturu,

1649
01:03:44,480 --> 01:03:45,740
 preiko skokoje,

1650
01:03:45,740 --> 01:03:47,440
 i jedno radijenje istraživanje,

1651
01:03:47,440 --> 01:03:49,240
 svako koliko ima kladionca u Mostaru.

1652
01:03:49,540 --> 01:03:50,820
 Nijem da je bilo svako deset metara.

1653
01:03:50,820 --> 01:03:53,120
 Čudi moji, koji je to otrov.

1654
01:03:53,120 --> 01:03:55,040
 Kako to razara obitelji?

1655
01:03:55,040 --> 01:03:56,140
 A za šta?

1656
01:03:56,140 --> 01:03:58,460
 Nek mi se javi samo jedan,

1657
01:03:58,460 --> 01:04:01,180
 koji je s kladioncom,

1658
01:04:01,180 --> 01:04:03,400
 ne oni koji vode kladionce,

1659
01:04:03,400 --> 01:04:05,280
 nego oni koji siglali kladioncu,

1660
01:04:05,280 --> 01:04:06,480
 da su profitirali,

1661
01:04:06,480 --> 01:04:08,040
 da su od toga nešto stvarili u životu.

1662
01:04:08,040 --> 01:04:09,960
 Nek mi se samo jedan javi.

1663
01:04:09,960 --> 01:04:11,180
 Iz Biblije kupi.

1664
01:04:11,180 --> 01:04:13,240
 Doćemo do toga dijela.

1665
01:04:13,240 --> 01:04:15,100
 Dobro, ja sam profitirao, ja, slučite.

1666
01:04:15,100 --> 01:04:17,000
 I, ovaj,

1667
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:19,520
 ja, ako tako gledam, istina je,

1668
01:04:19,540 --> 01:04:21,680
 i uglavnom,

1669
01:04:21,680 --> 01:04:23,860
 što je bilo,

1670
01:04:23,860 --> 01:04:26,200
 upisao sam fakultet,

1671
01:04:26,200 --> 01:04:27,940
 pa i to sam upisao,

1672
01:04:27,940 --> 01:04:30,160
 nekako volio sam kemiju,

1673
01:04:30,160 --> 01:04:32,340
 građevinska škola mi jako dobro išla,

1674
01:04:32,340 --> 01:04:33,720
 bio sam odlučan džak,

1675
01:04:33,720 --> 01:04:35,060
 matematiku nisam volio,

1676
01:04:35,060 --> 01:04:36,720
 pa nisam tijelo na građevinski fakultet,

1677
01:04:36,720 --> 01:04:37,600
 vam nije bilo prijemno,

1678
01:04:37,600 --> 01:04:38,640
 gajde ja će se probući

1679
01:04:38,640 --> 01:04:39,640
 i tu će upisati.

1680
01:04:39,640 --> 01:04:41,540
 I bilo je, evo, Bogu hvala,

1681
01:04:41,540 --> 01:04:42,400
 to je sve Boži prst,

1682
01:04:42,400 --> 01:04:43,500
 tako je trebalo i biti,

1683
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:45,380
 i upisao sam, evo,

1684
01:04:45,380 --> 01:04:46,680
 fakultet,

1685
01:04:46,680 --> 01:04:47,880
 dobro mi je tu išlo,

1686
01:04:47,940 --> 01:04:49,160
 uvijek sam bio dobar učenik,

1687
01:04:49,160 --> 01:04:51,460
 ali ta kocka je bila još prisutna.

1688
01:04:51,460 --> 01:04:53,740
 I jednom,

1689
01:04:53,740 --> 01:04:55,160
 moj prijatelj,

1690
01:04:55,160 --> 01:04:56,360
 koji je bio sa mnom,

1691
01:04:56,360 --> 01:04:58,660
 u izosnovne škole,

1692
01:04:58,660 --> 01:04:59,180
 prijatelj,

1693
01:04:59,180 --> 01:04:59,940
 danas smo prijatelji,

1694
01:04:59,940 --> 01:05:01,800
 i on je,

1695
01:05:01,800 --> 01:05:02,580
 rekao,

1696
01:05:02,580 --> 01:05:03,840
 on je upisao teologiju.

1697
01:05:03,840 --> 01:05:05,940
 Njegovama je bila u frizerskom salonu,

1698
01:05:05,940 --> 01:05:08,020
 a njegova mama,

1699
01:05:08,020 --> 01:05:09,320
 zanimljivo,

1700
01:05:09,320 --> 01:05:10,640
 ono,

1701
01:05:10,640 --> 01:05:12,000
 ucrkode ponekad žena,

1702
01:05:12,000 --> 01:05:13,320
 svako slučajno,

1703
01:05:13,320 --> 01:05:14,560
 zamestite kako Bog dijeluje

1704
01:05:14,560 --> 01:05:15,620
 na čudan način,

1705
01:05:15,620 --> 01:05:17,660
 preko ljudi koji možda nisu toliki vjernici.

1706
01:05:17,660 --> 01:05:18,240
 I ona je rekla,

1707
01:05:18,240 --> 01:05:19,660
 svome sinu,

1708
01:05:19,660 --> 01:05:20,560
 evo,

1709
01:05:20,560 --> 01:05:22,540
 ja sam čula od frizerke,

1710
01:05:22,540 --> 01:05:23,480
 teologija,

1711
01:05:23,480 --> 01:05:24,320
 odmah će ima posao,

1712
01:05:24,320 --> 01:05:25,060
 ajde ti to završi.

1713
01:05:25,060 --> 01:05:26,420
 On, nikakve veze s teologijom.

1714
01:05:26,420 --> 01:05:27,920
 Još manje nego ja.

1715
01:05:27,920 --> 01:05:28,520
 Nija,

1716
01:05:28,520 --> 01:05:29,220
 kamo li on?

1717
01:05:30,240 --> 01:05:32,520
 i on upiše teologiju,

1718
01:05:32,520 --> 01:05:33,800
 ja upišem akronomiju

1719
01:05:33,800 --> 01:05:35,900
 i nastavili smo mi normalno društi

1720
01:05:35,900 --> 01:05:37,800
 i meni društvo isto tako

1721
01:05:37,800 --> 01:05:39,760
 na fakultetu

1722
01:05:39,760 --> 01:05:41,380
 bilo je iz raznih krajeva svijeta,

1723
01:05:41,380 --> 01:05:43,100
 nisu više bili samo mostarci,

1724
01:05:43,100 --> 01:05:46,120
 iz raznih krajeva Hercegovine

1725
01:05:46,120 --> 01:05:47,700
 i poslije Hercegovine Hrvatske

1726
01:05:47,700 --> 01:05:50,220
 i dobri su bili momci,

1727
01:05:50,220 --> 01:05:51,540
 fino je to bilo društvo

1728
01:05:51,540 --> 01:05:53,180
 i danas smo evo nekad zajedno na okupu,

1729
01:05:53,180 --> 01:05:53,960
 evo mislim da idući tjedan

1730
01:05:53,960 --> 01:05:54,820
 smo se čak dogvarili

1731
01:05:54,820 --> 01:05:56,140
 za neko druženje

1732
01:05:56,140 --> 01:05:57,840
 i nekako sam,

1733
01:05:57,840 --> 01:05:58,780
 nisam ja nikad,

1734
01:05:58,780 --> 01:06:00,500
 osim što sam imao problema

1735
01:06:00,500 --> 01:06:01,640
 evo s tom kockom,

1736
01:06:01,640 --> 01:06:04,200
 nisam ja nikad bio tip

1737
01:06:04,200 --> 01:06:05,760
 koji će izići u grad,

1738
01:06:05,760 --> 01:06:06,620
 opijat se,

1739
01:06:06,620 --> 01:06:08,400
 dogodilo se par puta naravno,

1740
01:06:08,400 --> 01:06:12,060
 ali nije me to nekako ispunjalo,

1741
01:06:12,060 --> 01:06:12,420
 ne znam,

1742
01:06:12,420 --> 01:06:13,220
 više sam bio tip

1743
01:06:13,220 --> 01:06:14,700
 na neka kućna druženja,

1744
01:06:14,700 --> 01:06:16,740
 diskoteke i takve stvari,

1745
01:06:16,740 --> 01:06:19,120
 nije me to baš toliko zanimalo,

1746
01:06:19,120 --> 01:06:19,880
 ok, super,

1747
01:06:19,880 --> 01:06:21,000
 ali ne baš toliko.

1748
01:06:21,000 --> 01:06:24,860
 I tu se bio jedan prijatelj

1749
01:06:24,860 --> 01:06:25,860
 koji je uciro gitaru

1750
01:06:25,860 --> 01:06:26,640
 da sam ja tu počeo

1751
01:06:26,640 --> 01:06:27,560
 stanicirati gitaru

1752
01:06:27,560 --> 01:06:28,340
 na fakultetu

1753
01:06:28,340 --> 01:06:31,300
 i kockava sam im dalje

1754
01:06:31,300 --> 01:06:32,180
 naravno nastavio,

1755
01:06:32,180 --> 01:06:34,220
 ali to je bio ključ

1756
01:06:34,220 --> 01:06:35,240
 kako je se počelo.

1757
01:06:35,240 --> 01:06:36,320
 Ovaj prijatelj

1758
01:06:36,320 --> 01:06:37,820
 koji je upisao etologiju,

1759
01:06:37,820 --> 01:06:38,540
 sa njima je bila

1760
01:06:38,540 --> 01:06:39,420
 jedna časna sestra.

1761
01:06:39,420 --> 01:06:42,280
 I ona je ti je njemu rekla

1762
01:06:42,280 --> 01:06:44,060
 evo dole u Franjovačkoj

1763
01:06:44,060 --> 01:06:45,060
 crkvi u Mostaru

1764
01:06:45,060 --> 01:06:46,060
 jedan svećenik

1765
01:06:46,060 --> 01:06:46,780
 imala susrate,

1766
01:06:46,780 --> 01:06:47,540
 aj dođi ti.

1767
01:06:47,540 --> 01:06:48,960
 Sa njemu je bilo

1768
01:06:48,960 --> 01:06:50,600
 neugodno časnom sestru odbiti

1769
01:06:50,600 --> 01:06:52,020
 i on njima je rekao

1770
01:06:52,020 --> 01:06:52,460
 dođi,

1771
01:06:52,460 --> 01:06:53,520
 a ne bi on sam.

1772
01:06:53,520 --> 01:06:55,080
 I on mene zove,

1773
01:06:55,860 --> 01:06:57,300
 da baš si mene našao.

1774
01:06:57,300 --> 01:06:58,420
 No čovječe,

1775
01:06:58,420 --> 01:06:59,280
 pusti me na miru.

1776
01:06:59,280 --> 01:07:00,840
 Idem nedeljom u crkvu.

1777
01:07:00,840 --> 01:07:02,640
 Kako idem,

1778
01:07:02,640 --> 01:07:03,100
 to je sada

1779
01:07:03,100 --> 01:07:03,960
 druga stvar,

1780
01:07:03,960 --> 01:07:06,320
 ali kakva Franjovačka.

1781
01:07:06,320 --> 01:07:07,080
 Nisam znao,

1782
01:07:07,080 --> 01:07:07,640
 zamislite,

1783
01:07:07,640 --> 01:07:08,380
 meni je bilo 18 godina,

1784
01:07:08,380 --> 01:07:09,720
 nisam znao,

1785
01:07:09,720 --> 01:07:09,980
 ono,

1786
01:07:09,980 --> 01:07:10,780
 možda si čuva,

1787
01:07:10,780 --> 01:07:11,480
 ali to nije zanimalo,

1788
01:07:11,480 --> 01:07:11,620
 ono,

1789
01:07:11,620 --> 01:07:12,520
 to nije tvoj svijet.

1790
01:07:12,520 --> 01:07:14,620
 Nisam znao da postoji Franjovač,

1791
01:07:14,620 --> 01:07:15,600
 da postoji fratar,

1792
01:07:15,600 --> 01:07:16,600
 da postoji,

1793
01:07:16,600 --> 01:07:17,840
 da ja mogu biti

1794
01:07:17,840 --> 01:07:18,820
 svećenik uopće.

1795
01:07:19,280 --> 01:07:19,620
 Ja sam mislio,

1796
01:07:19,620 --> 01:07:20,740
 to su neki ljudi,

1797
01:07:20,740 --> 01:07:21,780
 gore s neba pali,

1798
01:07:21,780 --> 01:07:22,680
 to je to,

1799
01:07:22,680 --> 01:07:23,380
 to je njihovo,

1800
01:07:23,380 --> 01:07:24,120
 što ja imam s tim,

1801
01:07:24,120 --> 01:07:25,120
 pusti me na miru,

1802
01:07:25,120 --> 01:07:26,000
 ja sam svoju odradio,

1803
01:07:26,000 --> 01:07:26,500
 nedeljom.

1804
01:07:26,500 --> 01:07:28,460
 Ja sam otišao na mislu.

1805
01:07:28,460 --> 01:07:30,300
 Dobar sam vjerni,

1806
01:07:30,300 --> 01:07:30,860
 je li tako?

1807
01:07:30,860 --> 01:07:32,920
 Tako sam ja mislio,

1808
01:07:32,920 --> 01:07:33,780
 tako mnogi mislio,

1809
01:07:33,780 --> 01:07:34,560
 danas nažalost.

1810
01:07:35,360 --> 01:07:37,320
 I o meni nagovori.

1811
01:07:37,320 --> 01:07:38,380
 I to kako?

1812
01:07:38,380 --> 01:07:39,280
 Naravno,

1813
01:07:39,280 --> 01:07:40,120
 kako mi ljudi volimo

1814
01:07:40,120 --> 01:07:41,120
 neke ekstremne stvari,

1815
01:07:41,120 --> 01:07:41,800
 kažu o meni,

1816
01:07:41,800 --> 01:07:43,340
 taj svećenik ti prođe,

1817
01:07:43,340 --> 01:07:44,700
 onda mi svi nešto,

1818
01:07:44,700 --> 01:07:46,640
 molimo se,

1819
01:07:46,640 --> 01:07:47,520
 poslije srušimo,

1820
01:07:47,520 --> 01:07:48,460
 ono presvjeto,

1821
01:07:48,460 --> 01:07:48,620
 pa.

1822
01:07:48,620 --> 01:07:51,060
 Haj sa nimljubo,

1823
01:07:51,060 --> 01:07:51,500
 je odvode,

1824
01:07:51,500 --> 01:07:52,060
 a vidi šta je.

1825
01:07:52,060 --> 01:07:54,000
 Ja odem,

1826
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:56,620
 i to je bilo presudno.

1827
01:07:56,620 --> 01:07:58,400
 Zamislite da ja

1828
01:07:58,400 --> 01:07:59,640
 od tada

1829
01:07:59,640 --> 01:08:01,500
 nikad više,

1830
01:08:01,500 --> 01:08:03,420
 to što bili susretni za mlade,

1831
01:08:04,500 --> 01:08:05,620
 koje je odio jedan svećenik,

1832
01:08:05,620 --> 01:08:06,220
 Franjevac.

1833
01:08:06,220 --> 01:08:08,580
 Ja sam se

1834
01:08:08,580 --> 01:08:10,300
 toliko zaljubio

1835
01:08:10,300 --> 01:08:12,380
 u Kristove riječi

1836
01:08:12,380 --> 01:08:13,280
 koje je on izgovarao.

