2090
01:15:09,020 --> 01:15:11,840
 razilaženja u mišljenjima,

2091
01:15:11,840 --> 01:15:13,300
 ali kada imaš negadam,

2092
01:15:13,300 --> 01:15:14,160
 to sve kažeš,

2093
01:15:14,160 --> 01:15:16,140
 sve spane sa tebe.

2094
01:15:16,140 --> 01:15:20,160
 I ta osoba je meni predložila

2095
01:15:20,160 --> 01:15:22,320
 da ja krenem,

2096
01:15:22,320 --> 01:15:23,800
 evo, osim da vidim na sustrate,

2097
01:15:23,800 --> 01:15:25,900
 sad sam počuł fanjorski sjetovni red,

2098
01:15:25,900 --> 01:15:28,200
 da pođem četvrtkom na klanjanje.

2099
01:15:29,800 --> 01:15:34,080
 ističem to jer uz svetu misu,

2100
01:15:34,080 --> 01:15:35,080
 na drugom mjestu,

2101
01:15:35,080 --> 01:15:36,940
 najvažniji u našem životu,

2102
01:15:36,940 --> 01:15:37,680
 vjerujte mi je,

2103
01:15:37,680 --> 01:15:40,080
 za osobni rast i razvoj,

2104
01:15:40,940 --> 01:15:42,120
 buharistijsko klanjanje.

2105
01:15:42,120 --> 01:15:44,340
 Klanjanje presvetom utarskom sakramentu,

2106
01:15:44,340 --> 01:15:47,080
 kasnije ću spomenuti u svom životu,

2107
01:15:47,080 --> 01:15:48,840
 koliko mi je to bilo važno i značilo.

2108
01:15:50,040 --> 01:15:52,820
 I ja sam ti poslušao,

2109
01:15:52,820 --> 01:15:57,560
 jer kroz tu osobu je progovarao sigurno Bog

2110
01:15:57,560 --> 01:16:01,080
 i u moj život duboko zahvatio tako nje.

2111
01:16:01,080 --> 01:16:02,840
 I evo, s toga je hvala

2112
01:16:02,840 --> 01:16:04,900
 i neki je dobroj Bog blagoslovi i čuva

2113
01:16:04,900 --> 01:16:09,240
 i danas je veliki poticaj za sve u mom životu.

2114
01:16:09,240 --> 01:16:12,660
 I ono što je bilo važno kad sam krenu na klanjanje,

2115
01:16:12,660 --> 01:16:14,260
 otkriva mi se opet jedan novi svijet.

2116
01:16:14,260 --> 01:16:16,240
 Osim nedeljne mise,

2117
01:16:16,240 --> 01:16:17,360
 sad ima još taj susret,

2118
01:16:17,360 --> 01:16:18,800
 pa ide četvrtko na klanjanje,

2119
01:16:19,620 --> 01:16:20,640
 ali to klanjanje,

2120
01:16:20,640 --> 01:16:23,040
 taj susret sa živim gospodinom

2121
01:16:23,040 --> 01:16:26,140
 je nešto što je duboko mene mijenjalo iznutra.

2122
01:16:26,140 --> 01:16:27,600
 Možda nisam bio toga svjestan.

2123
01:16:27,600 --> 01:16:29,980
 I kad kreneš za gospodinom,

2124
01:16:29,980 --> 01:16:31,020
 kad te on zahvati,

2125
01:16:31,020 --> 01:16:33,480
 ti samo želiš još više.

2126
01:16:33,480 --> 01:16:37,360
 I malo pomalo krene fraz Zlatko

2127
01:16:37,360 --> 01:16:39,640
 i svaki dan na svetu misu.

2128
01:16:39,640 --> 01:16:44,180
 Puno protivljenja,

2129
01:16:44,180 --> 01:16:47,500
 ali imaš ljude koji su tu svaki dan u crkvi,

2130
01:16:47,500 --> 01:16:49,420
 skupa s tobom, nisi sam.

2131
01:16:49,420 --> 01:16:50,460
 Ne bojiš se.

2132
01:16:50,460 --> 01:16:52,960
 S druge strane pričaju,

2133
01:16:52,960 --> 01:16:54,440
 poludio, pomanito,

2134
01:16:54,440 --> 01:16:57,360
 vako, nako, ovakavije,

2135
01:16:57,360 --> 01:16:59,200
 onakavije, treba ga voditi u ludnicu.

2136
01:16:59,200 --> 01:17:00,700
 Kakva mu je dijagnoza?

2137
01:17:00,700 --> 01:17:01,960
 Ko svećenika su me vodili,

2138
01:17:01,960 --> 01:17:03,880
 da on stanovi da nisam dobar.

2139
01:17:03,880 --> 01:17:05,920
 Jedan on ima rekao,

2140
01:17:05,920 --> 01:17:07,520
 ne bojite se vide njega.

2141
01:17:08,840 --> 01:17:10,480
 Svaki tjedan sam se ispovijedao,

2142
01:17:10,480 --> 01:17:12,160
 išao na svetu misu,

2143
01:17:12,160 --> 01:17:12,940
 ja govorim to svećeniku,

2144
01:17:12,940 --> 01:17:13,700
 svećenik se smije,

2145
01:17:13,700 --> 01:17:14,940
 kaže on, pa što ste doveli,

2146
01:17:14,940 --> 01:17:15,600
 ja govorim, ne znam,

2147
01:17:15,600 --> 01:17:16,500
 bio sam poslušan,

2148
01:17:16,500 --> 01:17:17,260
 tijelo sam doći,

2149
01:17:17,260 --> 01:17:18,460
 da vi procijenite,

2150
01:17:18,460 --> 01:17:19,380
 je li sve u redu sa mnom.

2151
01:17:19,380 --> 01:17:21,340
 Tada još nisam bio u samostanu.

2152
01:17:22,920 --> 01:17:24,880
 I ta ljubav koju sam primio preg gospodina,

2153
01:17:24,880 --> 01:17:26,140
 to je nešto nevjerovatno.

2154
01:17:26,140 --> 01:17:27,280
 I naravno da sam ja,

2155
01:17:27,280 --> 01:17:28,220
 evo,

2156
01:17:28,220 --> 01:17:30,680
 kroz svakodnevnu svetu misu,

2157
01:17:30,680 --> 01:17:32,360
 koja je bila najveća milost svom životu,

2158
01:17:32,360 --> 01:17:33,820
 imao sam milost,

2159
01:17:33,820 --> 01:17:35,260
 ja bih rekao da je gospodin me,

2160
01:17:35,260 --> 01:17:35,880
 kao evo,

2161
01:17:35,880 --> 01:17:37,480
 kao svoje dijelo,

2162
01:17:37,480 --> 01:17:39,020
 kao glinu oblikovao,

2163
01:17:39,020 --> 01:17:41,040
 najviše je kroz ovu svetu misu,

2164
01:17:41,040 --> 01:17:41,740
 uharistiju,

2165
01:17:41,740 --> 01:17:42,860
 i kroz klanjanje.

2166
01:17:42,860 --> 01:17:44,980
 Osim klanjanje četvrtkom,

2167
01:17:44,980 --> 01:17:46,420
 saznao sam u Mostaru,

2168
01:17:46,420 --> 01:17:49,140
 i svima to sada želim staviti na srce,

2169
01:17:50,460 --> 01:17:51,380
 jedno prelijepo mjesto,

2170
01:17:51,380 --> 01:17:51,580
 evo,

2171
01:17:51,580 --> 01:17:53,280
 na mojoj pozivnici od mlade mise,

2172
01:17:53,280 --> 01:17:54,740
 nalazi se slika,

2173
01:17:54,740 --> 01:17:56,400
 koju sam ja ufotografirao,

2174
01:17:56,400 --> 01:17:58,900
 tabernakuliste moje kapelice,

2175
01:17:58,900 --> 01:18:00,300
 najdraže u kojoj sam provodio,

2176
01:18:00,300 --> 01:18:01,680
 dane i dane,

2177
01:18:01,680 --> 01:18:02,940
 saate i saate,

2178
01:18:02,940 --> 01:18:04,660
 pred gospodinom u molitvi.

2179
01:18:04,660 --> 01:18:07,300
 To je kapela klanjanja,

2180
01:18:07,300 --> 01:18:09,060
 u samostanu,

2181
01:18:09,060 --> 01:18:10,440
 časni se stara Franjevki,

2182
01:18:10,440 --> 01:18:13,020
 malo prije Franjevačke crke u Franjevačko ulici,

2183
01:18:13,020 --> 01:18:15,200
 i presveto je izloženo cijeli dan,

2184
01:18:15,200 --> 01:18:17,440
 sestre se po sat vremena mjenjaju,

2185
01:18:17,440 --> 01:18:18,780
 uvijek je neko pred presvetim,

2186
01:18:19,240 --> 01:18:20,000
 i od sestara,

2187
01:18:20,000 --> 01:18:23,000
 a naravno i narod Božji Puk isto uvijek može doći,

2188
01:18:23,000 --> 01:18:25,620
 mislim da je do šest najveće otvorena kapelica,

2189
01:18:25,620 --> 01:18:28,280
 i nedavno sam bio u posjeti s sestrama,

2190
01:18:28,280 --> 01:18:29,760
 jer kaj god sam u Mostaru,

2191
01:18:29,760 --> 01:18:31,180
 ja se vraćam tu na svoj izvor.

2192
01:18:31,180 --> 01:18:32,020
 Znači,

2193
01:18:32,020 --> 01:18:32,960
 Međugorje,

2194
01:18:32,960 --> 01:18:34,420
 sveta misa,

2195
01:18:34,420 --> 01:18:35,240
 klanjanje,

2196
01:18:35,240 --> 01:18:36,480
 kapelica Mostar,

2197
01:18:36,480 --> 01:18:37,760
 Podbrdo,

2198
01:18:37,760 --> 01:18:39,520
 Mladifest,

2199
01:18:40,040 --> 01:18:42,560
 to su mjesta gdje se moje duhovno zvanje oblikovalo,

2200
01:18:42,560 --> 01:18:44,280
 gdje me gospodin evo mijenjao,

2201
01:18:44,280 --> 01:18:46,980
 i sestre kažu,

2202
01:18:46,980 --> 01:18:48,740
 evo našega fra Zlatka,

2203
01:18:48,740 --> 01:18:50,880
 on je ovdje zvanje svoje tesao,

2204
01:18:50,880 --> 01:18:52,000
 i zaista je to tako,

2205
01:18:52,000 --> 01:18:53,060
 zaista je to tako,

2206
01:18:53,060 --> 01:18:55,280
 i ako želite promjenu u svom životu,

2207
01:18:55,280 --> 01:18:55,460
 nešto,

2208
01:18:55,560 --> 01:18:57,540
 bila kakav problem po teškoću imate,

2209
01:18:57,540 --> 01:19:00,240
 otvorena je kapelica,

2210
01:19:00,240 --> 01:19:01,480
 znači od 8 ujutru,

2211
01:19:01,480 --> 01:19:03,000
 do 6 posle podne,

2212
01:19:03,000 --> 01:19:04,980
 samo ti idete pred gospodina,

2213
01:19:04,980 --> 01:19:06,800
 i njemu sve iznesite,

2214
01:19:06,800 --> 01:19:07,920
 pred njim se osunčajte,

2215
01:19:07,920 --> 01:19:09,640
 koliko sam suza tamo prolio,

2216
01:19:09,640 --> 01:19:12,500
 po teškoća zbog osude,

2217
01:19:12,500 --> 01:19:15,660
 ti kad ljudi ti sva šta govore oko tebe,

2218
01:19:15,660 --> 01:19:17,220
 su donati šapće,

2219
01:19:17,220 --> 01:19:18,780
 jer stvarno je možda nešto tako,

2220
01:19:18,780 --> 01:19:21,880
 ali ti onda razlučuješ svoje stvari,

2221
01:19:21,880 --> 01:19:23,460
 kroz živi odnos,

2222
01:19:23,460 --> 01:19:25,080
 odnos sa živim Bogom,

2223
01:19:25,400 --> 01:19:26,400
 tako je kod mene bilo,

2224
01:19:26,400 --> 01:19:28,800
 i osim toga,

2225
01:19:28,800 --> 01:19:29,180
 naravno,

2226
01:19:29,180 --> 01:19:30,660
 istaknuo bih ove seminare,

2227
01:19:30,660 --> 01:19:32,020
 postamolite i šutnje,

2228
01:19:32,020 --> 01:19:33,400
 koje sam bio u Bijelom polju,

2229
01:19:33,400 --> 01:19:37,020
 kod časne sestre Ljilje Pehar,

2230
01:19:37,020 --> 01:19:38,100
 koji su također,

2231
01:19:38,100 --> 01:19:38,320
 evo,

2232
01:19:38,320 --> 01:19:39,860
 zaista ostavili velik trag,

2233
01:19:39,860 --> 01:19:40,580
 dubog trag,

2234
01:19:40,580 --> 01:19:41,320
 evo,

2235
01:19:41,320 --> 01:19:43,160
 za moje duhovno zvanje,

2236
01:19:43,160 --> 01:19:45,020
 ono što,

2237
01:19:45,020 --> 01:19:45,400
 evo,

2238
01:19:45,400 --> 01:19:46,300
 bih još rekao,

2239
01:19:46,300 --> 01:19:48,580
 prije nego sam,

2240
01:19:48,580 --> 01:19:49,720
 nikad nisam mislil,

2241
01:19:49,720 --> 01:19:50,400
 da ću otiči samost,

2242
01:19:50,400 --> 01:19:52,180
 sam bez obrža što sak je da išao na svetu misu,

2243
01:19:52,180 --> 01:19:53,880
 bilo je tu i simpatija,

2244
01:19:54,280 --> 01:19:56,720
 i neki djevojki i sviđanja svega ljubavi,

2245
01:19:56,720 --> 01:19:57,260
 evo,

2246
01:19:57,260 --> 01:19:59,180
 znam da to ljudi vole čuti od svećanika,

2247
01:19:59,180 --> 01:20:00,160
 pa evo,

2248
01:20:00,160 --> 01:20:00,940
 da isto spomenem,

2249
01:20:00,940 --> 01:20:03,620
 to je puno manje nevažna stvar,

2250
01:20:03,620 --> 01:20:04,240
 evo,

2251
01:20:04,240 --> 01:20:04,740
 gospodin,

2252
01:20:04,740 --> 01:20:05,200
 nas,

2253
01:20:05,200 --> 01:20:06,780
 ja bih rekao nekad,

2254
01:20:06,780 --> 01:20:09,160
 kogo želi biti svećanik,

2255
01:20:09,160 --> 01:20:10,260
 može biti svećanik,

2256
01:20:10,260 --> 01:20:11,480
 neće gospodin reći,

2257
01:20:11,480 --> 01:20:11,680
 e,

2258
01:20:11,680 --> 01:20:12,340
 ti ne možeš,

2259
01:20:12,340 --> 01:20:13,300
 mi nekad govorimo,

2260
01:20:13,300 --> 01:20:14,160
 ja isto sam sam,

2261
01:20:14,160 --> 01:20:15,240
 nekad bi uvjeren,

2262
01:20:15,720 --> 01:20:16,480
 i sada sam naravno,

2263
01:20:16,480 --> 01:20:17,400
 treba što ima poziv,

2264
01:20:17,400 --> 01:20:19,760
 ali jes li izmolio taj poziv?

2265
01:20:19,760 --> 01:20:22,520
 Nije se mi poziv dogodio prekonaći,

2266
01:20:22,520 --> 01:20:24,860
 trebalo je proći fazu čišćenja,

2267
01:20:24,860 --> 01:20:25,620
 obraćenja,

2268
01:20:25,620 --> 01:20:27,160
 ali gdje je gospodin mijenjao?

2269
01:20:27,160 --> 01:20:28,380
 Susretoć njim,

2270
01:20:28,380 --> 01:20:29,940
 svetoj uharisti,

2271
01:20:29,940 --> 01:20:31,360
 svetoj pričesti,

2272
01:20:31,360 --> 01:20:32,820
 ispredaonici.

2273
01:20:34,620 --> 01:20:37,680
 I ono što je jako važno,

2274
01:20:37,680 --> 01:20:38,000
 evo,

2275
01:20:38,000 --> 01:20:40,260
 istaknuti još u moj duhovnom pozivu,

2276
01:20:40,260 --> 01:20:41,400
 rekao sam ovi seminari,

2277
01:20:41,400 --> 01:20:43,480
 gdje ti osobno susredneš zboga,

2278
01:20:43,480 --> 01:20:45,720
 i nisam ni sanjao,

2279
01:20:45,720 --> 01:20:46,380
 ni mislio tada,

2280
01:20:46,380 --> 01:20:47,260
 da će sve te stvari,

2281
01:20:47,260 --> 01:20:48,340
 koje su meni oblikovale,

2282
01:20:48,340 --> 01:20:51,480
 kašim je gospodin mene upotrebljavati,

2283
01:20:51,480 --> 01:20:52,720
 na iste te načine,

2284
01:20:52,720 --> 01:20:54,480
 da ja druge dogodim njemu.

2285
01:20:54,480 --> 01:20:55,980
 To mi je bilo fascinantno,

2286
01:20:55,980 --> 01:20:56,860
 kad sam se zaredio.

2287
01:20:56,860 --> 01:20:58,460
 I kažem,

2288
01:20:58,460 --> 01:20:58,980
 sve te simpatije,

2289
01:20:58,980 --> 01:21:00,500
 ljubav i prolazne,

2290
01:21:00,500 --> 01:21:01,460
 sve to dobro bilo.

2291
01:21:01,460 --> 01:21:02,100
 Naravno,

2292
01:21:02,100 --> 01:21:02,960
 čovjek sam bio,

2293
01:21:03,040 --> 01:21:04,220
 sto puta zaljubljen.

2294
01:21:04,220 --> 01:21:06,900
 I dogodi se jednostavno,

2295
01:21:06,900 --> 01:21:07,680
 i napast,

2296
01:21:07,680 --> 01:21:08,120
 i sve,

2297
01:21:08,120 --> 01:21:09,600
 ali nema ništa u tome ni loše.

2298
01:21:09,600 --> 01:21:12,980
 Ali kad čovjek sva ti svojim razumom,

2299
01:21:12,980 --> 01:21:14,000
 kad dokučiš,

2300
01:21:14,000 --> 01:21:15,680
 radi ići svoje osjećaje.

2301
01:21:15,680 --> 01:21:18,180
 Radi ići svoje osjećaje.

2302
01:21:18,180 --> 01:21:19,680
 Oni su nekada varljivi,

2303
01:21:19,680 --> 01:21:21,840
 mogu to desiti na krivi put.

2304
01:21:21,840 --> 01:21:24,400
 Oti iđi pred gospodina,

2305
01:21:24,400 --> 01:21:24,920
 pita njega,

2306
01:21:24,920 --> 01:21:25,760
 a što je njegova volja?

2307
01:21:25,760 --> 01:21:27,320
 I ja sam zapravo nesvjesno,

2308
01:21:27,320 --> 01:21:28,180
 sve te godine,

2309
01:21:28,180 --> 01:21:30,280
 molio jednu molitvu svetoga Franje,

2310
01:21:30,280 --> 01:21:31,840
 koja kaže,

2311
01:21:31,960 --> 01:21:32,400
 gospodine,

2312
01:21:32,400 --> 01:21:33,180
 što je tvoja volja?

2313
01:21:33,180 --> 01:21:34,440
 Što želiš da učinim?

2314
01:21:34,440 --> 01:21:36,260
 Ja sam to molio,

2315
01:21:36,260 --> 01:21:36,980
 ja sam te kasnije shvatio,

2316
01:21:36,980 --> 01:21:37,280
 joj čovječ,

2317
01:21:37,280 --> 01:21:38,560
 ja sam molio Božu volju,

2318
01:21:38,560 --> 01:21:40,640
 nikad nisam znao da molim za nju.

2319
01:21:40,640 --> 01:21:41,340
 Nesvjesno,

2320
01:21:41,340 --> 01:21:42,120
 bila mi je molitva

2321
01:21:42,120 --> 01:21:43,740
 u mom revijaru,

2322
01:21:43,740 --> 01:21:44,740
 časoslovu,

2323
01:21:44,740 --> 01:21:45,940
 koje sam molili kao član

2324
01:21:45,940 --> 01:21:47,960
 Franjačkog srednog reda

2325
01:21:47,960 --> 01:21:48,500
 iz Mostara.

2326
01:21:49,960 --> 01:21:51,500
 i ta molitva je zaista

2327
01:21:51,500 --> 01:21:52,880
 čuda učinila.

2328
01:21:52,880 --> 01:21:54,940
 I tako da sam

2329
01:21:54,940 --> 01:21:57,500
 uz sve te poteškoće,

2330
01:21:57,500 --> 01:21:59,060
 uz nerazumijevanja,

2331
01:21:59,060 --> 01:22:00,400
 brojnih ljudi imao

2332
01:22:00,400 --> 01:22:02,500
 i gospodin uvijek pošalje nekoga

2333
01:22:02,500 --> 01:22:04,240
 ko će te upraviti na pravi put,

2334
01:22:04,240 --> 01:22:05,100
 ko će ti pomoći.

2335
01:22:06,180 --> 01:22:07,420
 I tako sam uvijek ja,

2336
01:22:07,420 --> 01:22:08,500
 ja sjećam iza mise,

2337
