 ovdje na zemlji,

2556
01:27:51,240 --> 01:27:52,900
 da ćemo živjeti lagodno.

2557
01:27:52,900 --> 01:27:53,780
 On kaže,

2558
01:27:53,780 --> 01:27:54,560
