2563
01:28:04,260 --> 01:28:05,820
 ono što ne propada,

2564
01:28:05,820 --> 01:28:07,500
 a ovdje sve prolazi,

2565
01:28:07,500 --> 01:28:08,740
 sve prolazi.

2566
01:28:09,740 --> 01:28:11,120
 I tako je ta Franjina,

2567
01:28:11,120 --> 01:28:12,100
