 i jednoj sam osobi,

2844
01:35:55,440 --> 01:35:56,580
 se povjerio naravno,

2845
01:35:56,580 --> 01:35:58,220
 rekao što mi se dogodilo,

2846
01:35:58,220 --> 01:36:00,240
 ona je rekla,

2847
01:36:00,240 --> 01:36:01,120
 lijepo,

2848
01:36:01,120 --> 01:36:01,720
 super,

2849
01:36:01,720 --> 01:36:03,080
 i,

2850
01:36:03,080 --> 01:36:04,160
 ono,

2851
01:36:04,160 --> 01:36:04,500
 rekao,

2852
01:36:04,500 --> 01:36:05,720
 nastavit ću ja molit se dalje.

2853
01:36:06,500 --> 01:36:07,600
 dolaze pred duhove,

2854
01:36:07,600 --> 01:36:09,880
 ja idem na seminar s mladima u Međugorje,

2855
01:36:09,880 --> 01:36:11,460
 i,

2856
01:36:11,460 --> 01:36:13,880
 sad se dogodi jedan važan trenutak.

2857
01:36:15,420 --> 01:36:16,540
 dolaze jedanog svećanika,

2858
01:36:16,540 --> 01:36:17,860
 velik red kod njega.

2859
01:36:17,860 --> 01:36:19,780
 Pa rekao,

2860
01:36:19,780 --> 01:36:20,460
 ja joj ostati ću ovdje,

2861
01:36:20,460 --> 01:36:21,740
 neći sad ništa premješat se,

2862
01:36:21,740 --> 01:36:21,940
 ono,

2863
01:36:21,940 --> 01:36:22,440
 ide red,

2864
01:36:22,440 --> 01:36:24,560
 drugi svećanici svećinom već bili malo,

2865
01:36:24,560 --> 01:36:24,740
 ono,

2866
01:36:24,740 --> 01:36:25,180
 razišli,

2867
01:36:25,180 --> 01:36:25,660
 otišli,

2868
01:36:25,660 --> 01:36:27,940
 to je bilo tamo gdje su bile stari,

2869
01:36:27,940 --> 01:36:28,640
 ispred oncevenove,

2870
01:36:28,640 --> 01:36:29,880
 još nisu bili izgrađene.

2871
01:36:30,700 --> 01:36:32,380
 Vidim ja slovenski i hrvatski,

2872
01:36:32,380 --> 01:36:34,360
 on se zove da Nikola Rupnik,

2873
01:36:34,360 --> 01:36:38,680
 i ja sam te kasnije saznao da on ima još taj posljedni dar,

2874
01:36:38,680 --> 01:36:40,360
 Boži čitanja ljudskog srca,

2875
01:36:40,360 --> 01:36:41,640
 i on men kaže,

2876
01:36:41,640 --> 01:36:42,100
 moliti,

2877
01:36:42,100 --> 01:36:43,840
 to je bilo pred duhove,

2878
01:36:43,840 --> 01:36:45,400
 mi je još počeo taj seminar,

2879
01:36:45,400 --> 01:36:45,720
 kaže,

2880
01:36:45,720 --> 01:36:47,040
 moliti dvecu duhu svetom,

2881
01:36:47,040 --> 01:36:48,800
 razlučenje svog poziva,

2882
01:36:48,800 --> 01:36:49,200
 i tako,

2883
01:36:49,200 --> 01:36:49,660
 i tako,

2884
01:36:49,660 --> 01:36:51,980
 između ostalog mi je to rekao,

2885
01:36:51,980 --> 01:36:53,040
 ali,

2886
01:36:53,040 --> 01:36:55,580
 ja vam ne mogu pisati to jedna,

2887
01:36:55,580 --> 01:36:57,020
 kad ima,

2888
01:36:57,020 --> 01:36:57,500
 ja volio,

2889
01:36:57,500 --> 01:36:58,540
 neki ljudi kažu,

2890
01:36:59,120 --> 01:37:00,320
 nisam doživio ispovjed,

2891
01:37:00,320 --> 01:37:00,700
 po ništa,

2892
01:37:00,700 --> 01:37:01,140
 ono,

2893
01:37:01,140 --> 01:37:01,980
 čovjek me odriješio,

2894
01:37:01,980 --> 01:37:02,780
 nisam ništa osjetio,

2895
01:37:02,780 --> 01:37:03,820
 ne morati osjetiti,

2896
01:37:03,820 --> 01:37:06,620
 ja nikad nakon toga nisam ništa posebno osjetio,

2897
01:37:06,620 --> 01:37:08,660
 ali znam da sam se ispovjedio,

2898
01:37:08,660 --> 01:37:10,220
 i,

2899
01:37:10,220 --> 01:37:11,820
 ta ispovjed je bila preposna,

2900
01:37:11,820 --> 01:37:13,620
 još sam se ja kasnije par puta kod njega ispovjedio,

2901
01:37:13,620 --> 01:37:15,220
 ali ta prva je bila čudesna,

2902
01:37:15,220 --> 01:37:17,220
 ja prvi put,

2903
01:37:17,220 --> 01:37:18,200
 sam tada osjetio,

2904
01:37:18,200 --> 01:37:20,180
 kao da sam stajao ispred Krista,

2905
01:37:20,180 --> 01:37:22,260
 ja sam tijel njega uzeti vjeru,

2906
01:37:22,260 --> 01:37:23,280
 i te misije ispred Once,

2907
01:37:23,280 --> 01:37:24,000
 ukrasti,

2908
01:37:24,640 --> 01:37:26,140
 i ponijeti za sobom kući,

2909
01:37:26,140 --> 01:37:28,540
 toliko je to bilo snažno,

2910
01:37:28,540 --> 01:37:29,740
 toliko je to bilo milosno,

2911
01:37:29,740 --> 01:37:30,980
 šta god da je rekao,

2912
01:37:30,980 --> 01:37:31,680
 ja je poslušao,

2913
01:37:31,680 --> 01:37:32,900
 ja sam njemu rekao za to,

2914
01:37:32,900 --> 01:37:33,980
 što mi se dogodilo,

2915
01:37:33,980 --> 01:37:35,120
 ovaj,

2916
01:37:35,120 --> 01:37:36,540
 na klanjanju,

2917
01:37:36,540 --> 01:37:36,860
 on govori,

2918
01:37:36,860 --> 01:37:37,540
 samo ti moli,

2919
01:37:39,540 --> 01:37:40,100
 međutim,

2920
01:37:40,100 --> 01:37:41,400
 prošlo je već neki,

2921
01:37:41,400 --> 01:37:43,920
 ja sam nastavio moliti u devetnicu duhu svetom,

2922
01:37:43,920 --> 01:37:46,600
 koja mi je danas jedna odraži molitvi,

2923
01:37:46,600 --> 01:37:52,520
 i jednostavno se počelo i dalje na klanjanju događati,

2924
01:37:52,520 --> 01:37:54,240
 da jednostavno,

2925
01:37:54,240 --> 01:37:56,360
 sad počinje mi ja malo željeti to,

2926
01:37:56,360 --> 01:37:58,240
 negdje se rađa to u meni,

2927
01:37:58,240 --> 01:37:59,140
 a s druge strane,

2928
01:37:59,140 --> 01:38:01,080
 pa ne znam baš,

2929
01:38:01,080 --> 01:38:03,380
 a ono znam uvijek i za mislje prije strane,

2930
01:38:03,380 --> 01:38:03,820
 jer s ljudima,

2931
01:38:03,820 --> 01:38:04,760
 ono sigurno bit će svećnik,

2932
01:38:04,760 --> 01:38:05,800
 ja nema šanse,

2933
01:38:05,800 --> 01:38:06,320
 ono,

2934
01:38:06,320 --> 01:38:07,840
 neću i to je to,

2935
01:38:09,060 --> 01:38:11,760
 i to se sve kroz par mjeseća odiralo,

2936
01:38:11,760 --> 01:38:12,460
 to je bilo,

2937
01:38:12,460 --> 01:38:13,400
 vam reći kratko,

2938
01:38:13,400 --> 01:38:14,300
 ali meni predugo,

2939
01:38:14,300 --> 01:38:16,220
 konta me nakon mi svi govore,

2940
01:38:16,220 --> 01:38:17,320
 da nisam dobar,

2941
01:38:17,320 --> 01:38:18,180
 da uvijek se namislim,

2942
01:38:18,180 --> 01:38:19,620
 sve sam šta kažem prije svećenika,

2943
01:38:19,620 --> 01:38:23,340
 i ništa uglavnom,

2944
01:38:23,340 --> 01:38:25,000
 ajde, ja sam nastavio moliti,

2945
01:38:25,000 --> 01:38:26,180
 ovdje mi ja opet kod njegovna ispovjed,

2946
01:38:26,180 --> 01:38:27,300
 sada pred duhove,

2947
01:38:27,300 --> 01:38:30,360
 je bilo u Međugorju,

2948
01:38:30,360 --> 01:38:31,460
 imao sam seminar,

2949
01:38:31,460 --> 01:38:33,220
 i bilo je duhovsko obdijenje,

2950
01:38:33,220 --> 01:38:35,360
 i mi smo se otešli neki ispovjedit,

2951
01:38:35,400 --> 01:38:37,240
 ja sam svima preporučio ispovjedit kod ga svećenika,

2952
01:38:37,240 --> 01:38:40,180
 i svojim braći i sestrama iz trećeg reda,

2953
01:38:40,180 --> 01:38:43,060
 i oni su isto obdježivjeli jako lijepi ispovjed kod njega,

2954
01:38:43,060 --> 01:38:45,100
 ali evo sad se vratim na svoje,

2955
01:38:47,220 --> 01:38:49,780
 i ja sam tu, kroz tu devetnicu,

2956
01:38:49,780 --> 01:38:52,600
 ponovo još više osjetio Boži poziv.

2957
01:38:52,600 --> 01:38:55,160
 I kad sam došao njemu, kad sam rekao,

2958
01:38:55,160 --> 01:38:55,780
 on govori,

2959
01:38:55,780 --> 01:38:57,700
 ja sam to znao,

2960
01:38:57,700 --> 01:38:58,980
 kad sam te prvi put vidio,

2961
01:38:58,980 --> 01:39:01,640
 Bog nikog ne prisiljava,

2962
01:39:01,640 --> 01:39:03,640
 nisam ti želio otvoreno reći,

2963
01:39:03,640 --> 01:39:05,060
 ali ja sam vidio to u tebi,

2964
01:39:05,060 --> 01:39:06,520
 da ti imaš da je poziv.

2965
01:39:08,760 --> 01:39:09,980
 Dobro, super,

2966
01:39:09,980 --> 01:39:11,920
 rekao, lijepo, šta sad,

2967
01:39:11,920 --> 01:39:13,540
 kako, kuda,

2968
01:39:13,540 --> 01:39:16,420
 i naravno ja sam usto sve opet,

2969
01:39:16,420 --> 01:39:18,540
 svaki dan išao na svetu misu,

2970
01:39:18,540 --> 01:39:21,100
 nastavio u kapelici,

2971
01:39:21,100 --> 01:39:22,720
 još više vremena u Mostaru,

2972
01:39:22,720 --> 01:39:24,960
 provodio razgovoru sa ljudima

2973
01:39:24,960 --> 01:39:25,660
 koji su, evo,

2974
01:39:25,660 --> 01:39:28,380
 bili mi duhovno vodstvo u tim trenucima,

2975
01:39:28,380 --> 01:39:30,500
 i evo i sa svećenikom,

2976
01:39:30,500 --> 01:39:34,600
 i to je baš bilo jedno neobično razdoblje.

2977
01:39:34,600 --> 01:39:37,180
 U devetom mjesecu počinio poslatura,

2978
01:39:37,180 --> 01:39:41,000
 a ja još šest i sedmi mjesec,

2979
01:39:41,000 --> 01:39:42,760
 prošlo duhovi, prošlo sve,

2980
01:39:42,760 --> 01:39:45,560
 ono, naravno napasti,

2981
01:39:45,560 --> 01:39:47,300
 malo mišljaš, malo pusti,

2982
01:39:47,300 --> 01:39:49,500
 malo ajde bolan, ženi se,

2983
01:39:49,500 --> 01:39:51,660
 međuvremeno,

2984
01:39:51,660 --> 01:39:54,240
 tri cure mi se nabeli,

2985
01:39:54,240 --> 01:39:55,360
 hoće sa mnom na krvu.

2986
01:39:55,360 --> 01:39:59,180
 Ja, ok, super,

2987
01:39:59,180 --> 01:40:00,920
 što sad, naravno,

2988
01:40:00,920 --> 01:40:02,280
 ja sam otičao stanjima na kavu,

2989
01:40:02,280 --> 01:40:04,980
 rekao im da ću samostan,

2990
01:40:04,980 --> 01:40:06,180
 nisam sa svima, s nekima,

2991
01:40:06,760 --> 01:40:09,260
 i jedna je rekla,

2992
01:40:09,260 --> 01:40:10,520
 ako bude slušala,

2993
01:40:10,520 --> 01:40:11,220
 bit će zanimljivo,

2994
01:40:11,220 --> 01:40:11,720
 kaže ona,

2995
01:40:11,720 --> 01:40:12,380
 koga se goti,

2996
01:40:12,380 --> 01:40:12,800
 ja zaljubim,

2997
01:40:12,800 --> 01:40:13,440
 odde u fratri.

2998
01:40:13,440 --> 01:40:13,760
 Ja govorim,

2999
01:40:13,760 --> 01:40:15,220
 pa trebala smjelma reći,

3000
01:40:15,220 --> 01:40:16,600
 da sam siguran u svojoj poziv.

3001
01:40:17,480 --> 01:40:19,400
 I uglavnom,

3002
01:40:19,400 --> 01:40:21,920
 evo, to je te bila ljudske neke,

3003
01:40:21,920 --> 01:40:23,160
 evo, naravno,

3004
01:40:23,160 --> 01:40:23,740
 napasti,

3005
01:40:23,740 --> 01:40:24,380
 koje, evo,

3006
01:40:24,380 --> 01:40:26,080
 uvijek treba proći

3007
01:40:26,080 --> 01:40:27,220
 u tom životnom putu,

3008
01:40:27,220 --> 01:40:27,760
 pozivu.

3009
01:40:27,760 --> 01:40:29,380
 Nije mene to iskreno taj to ni zanimalo,

3010
01:40:29,380 --> 01:40:30,240
 ja sam, ono,

3011
01:40:30,240 --> 01:40:32,040
 bio sam čvrst u tome,

3012
01:40:32,040 --> 01:40:33,160
 što si više u molitvi,

3013
01:40:33,160 --> 01:40:34,500
 poštaješ sve čvršći.

3014
01:40:35,500 --> 01:40:36,200
 I, ovaj,

3015
01:40:36,200 --> 01:40:38,200
 ne znam se sad ni što porajem reći,

3016
01:40:38,200 --> 01:40:39,360
 idemo dalje,

3017
01:40:39,360 --> 01:40:39,600
 evo,

3018
01:40:39,600 --> 01:40:40,840
 kroz moju borbu,

3019
01:40:40,840 --> 01:40:43,720
 još jedan važan trenutak,

3020
01:40:43,720 --> 01:40:45,780
 ma sigurno,

3021
01:40:45,780 --> 01:40:46,360
 ono,

3022
01:40:46,360 --> 01:40:47,140
 upečatljiv,

3023
01:40:47,140 --> 01:40:48,000
 upečatljiv.

3024
01:40:48,000 --> 01:40:49,500
 Kroz Međugorje,

3025
01:40:49,500 --> 01:40:50,200
 kroz Mladifest,

3026
01:40:50,200 --> 01:40:51,000
 naravno sve to.

3027
01:40:51,000 --> 01:40:52,840
 Otećao sam,

3028
01:40:52,840 --> 01:40:53,480
 rekao ovako,

3029
01:40:53,480 --> 01:40:53,840
 Bože,

3030
01:40:53,840 --> 01:40:55,160
 dogovor.

3031
01:40:55,160 --> 01:40:57,100
 Sad će se prijaviti,

3032
01:40:57,100 --> 01:40:57,740
 u Bijelopolje,

3033
01:40:57,740 --> 01:40:58,700
 još jednom na seminar,

3034
01:40:58,700 --> 01:41:00,780
 postavamo odvej šutnje,

3035
01:41:00,780 --> 01:41:02,660
 sad neđenim da je bio sedmi mjesec,

3036
01:41:02,660 --> 01:41:04,140
 u devjetima postulatura,

3037
01:41:04,140 --> 01:41:04,780
 ok,

3038
01:41:05,500 --> 01:41:06,060
 ovaj,

3039
01:41:06,060 --> 01:41:07,920
 a ja sam već u,

3040
01:41:07,920 --> 01:41:11,960
 prije toga otišao na razgovor kod pre Stanka Meštata,

3041
01:41:11,960 --> 01:41:12,960
 da u postulaturi,

3042
01:41:12,960 --> 01:41:13,780
 i prije će,

3043
01:41:13,780 --> 01:41:15,080
 ja otiću u kapelicu,

3044
01:41:15,080 --> 01:41:16,460
 i rekao,

3045
01:41:16,460 --> 01:41:16,720
 super,

3046
01:41:16,720 --> 01:41:17,560
 idem u kapelicu,

3047
01:41:17,560 --> 01:41:18,460
 pomolite se,

3048
01:41:18,460 --> 01:41:19,960
 i ja sam tamo pomolim gore,

3049
01:41:19,960 --> 01:41:20,520
 evo, Bože,

3050
01:41:20,520 --> 01:41:22,040
 ja znam da to nije za mene,

3051
01:41:22,040 --> 01:41:23,460
 da ti mjene nisi izabrao,

3052
01:41:23,460 --> 01:41:24,520
 da ja to ne mogu,

3053
01:41:24,520 --> 01:41:28,440
 Stanko, nek mi kaže da ne mogu,

3054
01:41:28,440 --> 01:41:29,840
 i super, to će biti tvoj znak,

3055
01:41:29,840 --> 01:41:30,560
 ja dođem tamo,

3056
01:41:30,560 --> 01:41:30,760
 kaže,

3057
01:41:30,760 --> 01:41:31,240
 Stanko,

3058
01:41:31,240 --> 01:41:32,760
 pa gdje si ti dosad?

3059
01:41:33,280 --> 01:41:34,680
 Pa ti ćeš biti dobar svećenik,

3060
01:41:34,680 --> 01:41:35,420
 ja ono,

3061
01:41:35,420 --> 01:41:36,800
 dobro,

3062
01:41:36,800 --> 01:41:37,720
 nisam to očekival,

3063
01:41:37,720 --> 01:41:38,060
 dobro,

3064
01:41:38,060 --> 01:41:39,520
 i ništa nastavim,

3065
01:41:39,520 --> 01:41:40,700
 ja sad idem na taj seminar,

3066
01:41:40,700 --> 01:41:42,620
 i,

3067
01:41:42,620 --> 01:41:44,580
 četvrtak,

3068
01:41:44,580 --> 01:41:46,040
 večer je počinjeno seminar,

3069
01:41:46,040 --> 01:41:49,880
 i na seminar je tada bio jedan svećenik iz Hrvatske,

3070
01:41:50,440 --> 01:41:53,460
 koji je, evo, širio pobožnost prema božanskom milost srđu,

3071
01:41:53,460 --> 01:41:56,700
 i on je imao svet u misu,

3072
01:41:56,700 --> 01:41:57,720
 četvrtak večer,

3073
01:41:57,720 --> 01:41:59,920
 ja sam nekako ne teme njegovog izgleda,

3074
01:41:59,920 --> 01:42:01,300
 prije nego je počela misa,

3075
01:42:01,300 --> 01:42:02,140
 ono,

3076
01:42:02,140 --> 01:42:03,040
 u misli mi došlo,

3077
01:42:03,040 --> 01:42:04,960
 baš neki čudan lik,

3078
01:42:04,960 --> 01:42:06,260
 kad sam vidio na otaru,

3079
01:42:06,260 --> 01:42:06,480
 rekao,

3080
01:42:06,480 --> 01:42:07,240
 Bože, mi je prosto,

3081
01:42:07,240 --> 01:42:08,980
 i ovaj,

3082
01:42:08,980 --> 01:42:10,920
 i sutradan petak,

3083
01:42:12,320 --> 01:42:12,940
 i ovaj,

3084
01:42:12,940 --> 01:42:14,300
 niko ništa ne zna,

3085
01:42:14,300 --> 01:42:16,080
 ovo šta se događa u meni,

3086
01:42:16,080 --> 01:42:16,760
 kakve borbe,

3087
01:42:16,760 --> 01:42:18,520
 da razmišljamo o tome,

3088
01:42:18,520 --> 01:42:19,380
 da ćeći samostan,

3089
01:42:19,380 --> 01:42:20,420
 do pojedini ljudi,

3090
01:42:20,420 --> 01:42:21,860
 ali šira masa,

3091
01:42:21,860 --> 01:42:24,220
 i ja sad,

3092
01:42:24,220 --> 01:42:26,780
 oću na ispovijek od toga svećenika,

3093
01:42:26,780 --> 01:42:28,700
 i sad počinjujemo predavanje,

3094
01:42:28,700 --> 01:42:30,080
 četiri i popodne,

3095
01:42:30,080 --> 01:42:31,120
 predavanje počinje,

3096
01:42:31,120 --> 01:42:33,280
 ja govorim njemu,

3097
01:42:33,280 --> 01:42:35,260
 evo, sad sam ja na red za ispovijed,

3098
01:42:35,260 --> 01:42:36,340
 ali možemo mi kasnije,

3099
01:42:36,340 --> 01:42:38,120
 zato što, evo,

3100
01:42:38,120 --> 01:42:39,300
 predavanje će počne,

3101
01:42:39,300 --> 01:42:40,060
 pa ćemo propustiti,

3102
01:42:40,180 --> 01:42:41,360
 u meni govori, uđi,

3103
01:42:41,360 --> 01:42:43,200
 ja govorim, ok,

3104
01:42:43,200 --> 01:42:45,640
 i uđem ja unutra,

3105
01:42:45,640 --> 01:42:49,300
 i kaže o meni,

3106
01:42:49,300 --> 01:42:50,280
 prva rečenica,

3107
01:42:50,280 --> 01:42:52,840
 jes ti kad gledaš,

3108
01:42:52,840 --> 01:42:53,300
 ugledalo,

3109
01:42:53,300 --> 01:42:55,480
 ja se mislim u sebi,

3110
01:42:55,480 --> 01:42:57,260
 Zlatko, dobro se zaključiva,

3111
01:42:57,260 --> 01:42:58,140
 jako čudan lik,

3112
01:42:58,140 --> 01:42:59,700
 kakve su to pitanje,

3113
01:42:59,700 --> 01:43:00,420
 mislim se u sebi,

3114
01:43:00,420 --> 01:43:03,260
 kažem ja,

3115
01:43:03,260 --> 01:43:04,960
 pa reko svećenik,

3116
01:43:04,960 --> 01:43:05,460
 poštoješ,

3117
01:43:05,460 --> 01:43:06,000
 odgovorit ćeš,

3118
01:43:06,000 --> 01:43:06,360
 a govorim,

3119
01:43:06,360 --> 01:43:07,220
 pa jesom, što,

3120
01:43:07,220 --> 01:43:08,640
 čovjek, znači,

3121
01:43:08,640 --> 01:43:09,440
 ništa ne zna,

3122
01:43:09,500 --> 01:43:10,520
 došao iz Hrvatske,

3123
01:43:10,520 --> 01:43:11,280
 nema me pojma,

3124
01:43:11,280 --> 01:43:12,040
 ništa,

3125
01:43:12,040 --> 01:43:13,500
 ništa on ne zna o meni,

3126
01:43:13,500 --> 01:43:14,240
 ni kako se zovem,

3127
01:43:14,240 --> 01:43:14,860
 ni ništa drugo,

3128
01:43:14,860 --> 01:43:16,780
 prvo što me kaže,

3129
01:43:16,780 --> 01:43:17,740
 kad sam je rekao,

3130
01:43:17,740 --> 01:43:18,140
 gledam,

3131
01:43:18,140 --> 01:43:19,440
 kaže o meni,

3132
01:43:19,440 --> 01:43:21,060
 pa kad pogledaš se,

3133
01:43:21,060 --> 01:43:23,220
 jel ti vidiš,

3134
01:43:23,220 --> 01:43:25,160
 da ćeš ti biti svećenik,

3135
01:43:25,160 --> 01:43:26,920
 znači,

3136
01:43:26,920 --> 01:43:27,260
 ono,

3137
01:43:27,260 --> 01:43:28,820
 Bože,

3138
01:43:28,820 --> 01:43:30,720
 tražio sam znak,

3139
01:43:31,360 --> 01:43:32,520
 ali ovako očit,

3140
01:43:32,520 --> 01:43:34,320
 nisam očekivao,

3141
01:43:34,320 --> 01:43:37,000
 i ja se sjećam,

3142
01:43:37,000 --> 01:43:37,840
 pa normalno sam,

3143
01:43:37,840 --> 01:43:38,580
 da sam se isplakao,

3144
01:43:38,580 --> 01:43:39,440
 to ti je trebalo,

3145
01:43:39,440 --> 01:43:41,120
 kao poticaj neki,

3146
01:43:41,120 --> 01:43:42,560
 da kreneš Božim putem,

3147
01:43:42,560 --> 01:43:44,140
 i,

3148
01:43:44,140 --> 01:43:47,140
 točno taj trenutak,

3149
01:43:47,140 --> 01:43:47,720
 ne mogu zaboraviti,

3150
01:43:47,720 --> 01:43:48,780
 ni u kojoj prostoriji je bio,

3151
01:43:48,780 --> 01:43:49,840
 imao sam na sebi,

3152
01:43:49,840 --> 01:43:51,080
 majicu narančastonu,

3153
01:43:51,080 --> 01:43:52,400
 i sad čuvam urmaru,

3154
01:43:52,900 --> 01:43:54,320
 Frama Hercegovina,

3155
01:43:54,320 --> 01:43:55,460
 to je vjerovatno,

3156
01:43:55,460 --> 01:43:56,460
 sa nekog od ovih,

3157
01:43:56,460 --> 01:43:58,180
 Frama Festa,

3158
01:43:58,180 --> 01:43:58,880
 majica,

3159
01:43:58,880 --> 01:44:01,280
 iako nisam nikad bio član,

3160
01:44:01,280 --> 01:44:03,420
 ali posjećivao sam te Frama Feste,

3161
01:44:03,420 --> 01:44:04,440
 i,

3162
01:44:04,440 --> 01:44:05,680
 nezaboravno,

3163
01:44:05,680 --> 01:44:06,580
 nešto nezaboravno,

3164
01:44:06,580 --> 01:44:07,460
 nešto predivno,

3165
01:44:07,460 --> 01:44:07,820
 i kažem,

3166
01:44:07,820 --> 01:44:09,280
 ja uvijek volim reći,

3167
01:44:09,280 --> 01:44:10,240
 naravno,

3168
01:44:10,240 --> 01:44:11,080
 on je rekao sestri,

3169
01:44:11,080 --> 01:44:12,020
 sestra je rekla svima,

3170
01:44:12,020 --> 01:44:13,800
 i taj seminar vam je na kraju,

3171
01:44:13,800 --> 01:44:14,880
 postao molite i šutnje,

3172
01:44:14,880 --> 01:44:15,900
 postao seminar,

3173
01:44:15,900 --> 01:44:16,200
 ono,

3174
01:44:16,200 --> 01:44:16,840
 priče,

3175
01:44:16,840 --> 01:44:17,820
 pjevanja,

3176
01:44:17,820 --> 01:44:18,340
 plesa,

3177
01:44:18,340 --> 01:44:19,080
 druženja,

3178
01:44:19,080 --> 01:44:20,920
 jer su svi shvatili,

3179
01:44:21,060 --> 01:44:22,220
 da ja idem u svećenike,

3180
01:44:22,220 --> 01:44:22,660
 da, evo,

3181
01:44:22,660 --> 01:44:23,540
 rad mišljam o tome,

3182
01:44:23,540 --> 01:44:26,060
 a ja na kraju ne otići sad,

3183
01:44:26,060 --> 01:44:26,760
 kad svi znaju,

3184
01:44:26,760 --> 01:44:27,620
 i,

3185
01:44:27,620 --> 01:44:28,100
 ovaj,

3186
01:44:28,100 --> 01:44:28,660
 ali dobro,

3187
01:44:28,660 --> 01:44:29,220
 šalim se otićem,

3188
01:44:29,220 --> 01:44:29,580
 naravno,

3189
01:44:29,580 --> 01:44:29,980
 svakako,

3190
01:44:29,980 --> 01:44:31,240
 jer takav znak,

3191
01:44:31,240 --> 01:44:32,220
 toliki znak,

3192
01:44:32,220 --> 01:44:33,520
 pa mislim da,

3193
01:44:33,520 --> 01:44:35,640
 ne da šta više pričati,

3194
01:44:35,640 --> 01:44:36,760
 i,

3195
01:44:36,760 --> 01:44:37,180
 ovaj,

3196
01:44:37,180 --> 01:44:37,800
 i evo,

3197
01:44:37,800 --> 01:44:38,900
 to je bilo nešto konačno,

3198
01:44:38,900 --> 01:44:40,600
 kasnije,

3199
01:44:40,600 --> 01:44:40,860
 evo,

3200
01:44:40,860 --> 01:44:42,540
 saznali su i ostali,

3201
01:44:42,540 --> 01:44:43,940
 počeo sam malo govoriti ljudima,

3202
01:44:43,940 --> 01:44:44,820
 da idemo u kostalatur,

3203
01:44:44,820 --> 01:44:45,940
 da idemo u samostan,

3204
01:44:46,560 --> 01:44:47,360
 neki sam malo borili,

3205
01:44:47,360 --> 01:44:49,280
 borili da ne odem na rašte načine,

3206
01:44:49,280 --> 01:44:51,260
 nije to dobro,

3207
01:44:51,260 --> 01:44:52,200
 ne valja za tebe,

3208
01:44:52,200 --> 01:44:52,520
 ovako,

3209
01:44:52,520 --> 01:44:52,920
 onako,

3210
01:44:52,920 --> 01:44:53,720
 pa evo,

3211
01:44:53,720 --> 01:44:54,180
 imaš sve,

3212
01:44:54,180 --> 01:44:54,360
 evo,

3213
01:44:54,360 --> 01:44:55,000
 da ćemo ti ovo,

3214
01:44:55,000 --> 01:44:55,820
 da ćemo ti ono,

3215
01:44:55,820 --> 01:44:56,660
 ja govoru,

3216
01:44:56,660 --> 01:44:57,220
 ljudi moji,

3217
01:44:57,220 --> 01:44:58,980
 cijeli svijet,

3218
01:44:58,980 --> 01:45:00,840
 gospodina mog zamijeniti,

3219
01:45:00,840 --> 01:45:01,200
 ne može,

3220
01:45:01,480 --> 01:45:06,040
 ti nemoš to opisać čovjeku koji nije u tome potpuno zaranjenu molitvu,

3221
01:45:06,040 --> 01:45:08,840
 pač meni je to smiješno bilo,

3222
01:45:08,840 --> 01:45:10,200
 bilo kakve obećanja,

3223
01:45:10,200 --> 01:45:11,480
 bilo šta prolazno,

3224
01:45:11,480 --> 01:45:14,900
 ne možeš mi dati više nego gospodin mi može dati,

3225
01:45:14,900 --> 01:45:16,060
 i evo,

3226
01:45:16,060 --> 01:45:17,640
 tako se rodio taj moj poziv,

3227
01:45:17,640 --> 01:45:20,060
 otišao sam u postlaturu,

3228
01:45:20,060 --> 01:45:21,560
 u Mostar,

3229
01:45:21,560 --> 01:45:23,120
 tu sam proveo deset mjeseci,

3230
01:45:23,120 --> 01:45:24,800
 opukao svoj habit,

3231
01:45:24,800 --> 01:45:26,160
 evo,

3232
01:45:26,160 --> 01:45:27,920
 još ću tu par stvari ispričati,

3233
01:45:27,920 --> 01:45:29,120
 ono,

3234
01:45:29,120 --> 01:45:30,080
 uvijek misliš ušao si,

3235
01:45:30,080 --> 01:45:30,740
 sad je to gotovo,

3236
01:45:30,800 --> 01:45:32,060
 naravno borbe se nastavile,

3237
01:45:32,060 --> 01:45:35,280
 na osobnom polju duhovnosti,

3238
01:45:35,280 --> 01:45:37,560
 i sjećam se pred oblačenje,

3239
01:45:37,560 --> 01:45:38,880
 jedna zanimljiva stvar,

3240
01:45:38,880 --> 01:45:42,160
 držim ja ovako,

3241
01:45:42,160 --> 01:45:43,760
 u Duvno je bilo Tomislav gradu,

3242
01:45:43,760 --> 01:45:44,200
 u crkvi,

3243
01:45:44,200 --> 01:45:45,120
 držim habit rukama,

3244
01:45:45,120 --> 01:45:46,480
 sad su mi trebali ući u procesiji,

3245
01:45:46,480 --> 01:45:51,300
 takav košmar u glavi,

3246
01:45:51,300 --> 01:45:52,640
 samo džava može napraviti,

3247
01:45:52,640 --> 01:45:53,260
 niko drugi,

3248
01:45:53,260 --> 01:45:55,260
 i to treba prepoznati duhove,

3249
01:45:55,260 --> 01:45:55,940
 ljudi,

3250
01:45:55,940 --> 01:45:58,300
 kad imate u glavi nered,

3251
01:45:58,300 --> 01:45:59,140
 nesloženost,

3252
01:45:59,140 --> 01:46:00,180
 otićete pred gospodina,

3253
01:46:00,180 --> 01:46:02,700
 nemojte nikad donosti naglo odluke,

3254
01:46:02,700 --> 01:46:05,440
 evo u tom trenutku,

3255
01:46:05,440 --> 01:46:05,920
 Bogu hvala,

3256
01:46:05,920 --> 01:46:07,040
 pa nisam donio naglo odluku,

3257
01:46:07,040 --> 01:46:08,380
 jako bi, evo,

3258
01:46:08,380 --> 01:46:10,640
 gospodin je se pobrnuo da to se bude dobro,

3259
01:46:10,640 --> 01:46:12,400
 ali je pustio malo,

3260
01:46:12,400 --> 01:46:12,840
 što kaže,

3261
01:46:12,840 --> 01:46:13,340
 napasta,

3262
01:46:13,340 --> 01:46:13,520
 evo,

3263
01:46:13,520 --> 01:46:14,100
 neg dođe,

3264
01:46:14,100 --> 01:46:14,900
 neg nekuša,

3265
01:46:15,700 --> 01:46:16,580
 i ja sam stajao,

3266
01:46:16,580 --> 01:46:19,480
 ja ne znam kako ja iz toga,

3267
01:46:19,480 --> 01:46:21,100
 iz te procese nisam izašao,

3268
01:46:21,100 --> 01:46:22,360
 jer sve u meni,

3269
01:46:22,360 --> 01:46:23,140
 sve u mojej glavi,

3270
01:46:23,140 --> 01:46:24,240
 u mojim islama je govorilo,

3271
01:46:24,240 --> 01:46:25,240
 ovo nije za tebe,

3272
01:46:25,240 --> 01:46:26,900
 iziđi iz ove procesije,

3273
01:46:26,900 --> 01:46:28,260
 ne ulazi u crkvu,

3274
01:46:29,500 --> 01:46:29,760
 ok,

3275
01:46:29,760 --> 01:46:31,560
 slušaš to cijelo vrijeme u glavi,

3276
01:46:31,560 --> 01:46:32,520
 napast,

3277
01:46:32,520 --> 01:46:34,740
 i držiš habit i ulaziš,

3278
01:46:34,740 --> 01:46:36,680
 onda uđeš u crkvu,

3279
01:46:36,680 --> 01:46:39,840
 i točno kad je počeo na zvuk orgulja,

3280
01:46:39,840 --> 01:46:41,280
 uff,

3281
01:46:41,280 --> 01:46:42,560
 samo spade sve sa mene,

3282
01:46:42,560 --> 01:46:44,500
 tisuću kila,

3283
01:46:44,500 --> 01:46:45,220
 vjerujem mi,

3284
01:46:45,220 --> 01:46:46,260
 tisuću kila,

3285
01:46:46,260 --> 01:46:49,380
 i od toga trenutka kad sam čuo taj zvuk orgulja,

3286
01:46:49,380 --> 01:46:51,040
 tijelo mi je prestala ta napast,

3287
01:46:51,040 --> 01:46:51,680
 i evo,

3288
01:46:51,680 --> 01:46:52,220
 Bogu hvala,

3289
01:46:52,220 --> 01:46:53,220
 obukao sam habit,

3290
01:46:53,220 --> 01:46:55,300
 probao sam zatim u novicijatu,

3291
01:46:55,300 --> 01:46:56,500
 ovaj,

3292
01:46:56,500 --> 01:46:57,600
 godinu dana,

3293
01:46:58,200 --> 01:47:00,920
 položio svoje prve prevremene zavijete tamo,

3294
01:47:00,920 --> 01:47:02,140
 naravno,

3295
01:47:02,140 --> 01:47:02,880
 i tu je bilo,

3296
01:47:02,880 --> 01:47:03,180
 ono,

3297
01:47:03,180 --> 01:47:05,580
 par nekih sitnih napasti na puštanju,

3298
01:47:05,580 --> 01:47:05,880
 a,

3299
01:47:05,880 --> 01:47:06,700
 evo,

3300
01:47:06,700 --> 01:47:07,240
 ajmo reći,

3301
01:47:07,240 --> 01:47:10,000
 neka najveća iduća je bila,

3302
01:47:10,000 --> 01:47:11,600
 pred moje doživotne zavijete.

3303
01:47:11,600 --> 01:47:16,080
 U Zagrebu sam normalno studirao,

3304
01:47:16,080 --> 01:47:16,640
 ideš na studij,

3305
01:47:16,640 --> 01:47:17,260
 ideš na faks,

3306
01:47:17,260 --> 01:47:17,900
 teologija,

3307
01:47:17,900 --> 01:47:18,440
 sve dobro,

3308
01:47:18,440 --> 01:47:19,040
 sve uredno,

3309
01:47:19,040 --> 01:47:22,740
 ali možda najveća poteškoća mi je bila pred zavijete,

3310
01:47:22,740 --> 01:47:24,860
 kad završavam četvrtu godinu,

3311
01:47:24,860 --> 01:47:26,240
 mi je da polažimo doživotne zavijete,

3312
01:47:27,500 --> 01:47:29,620
 i ja sam odgovarao sa svojim odgojiteljima,

3313
01:47:29,620 --> 01:47:31,620
 i rekao da sam da želim otkoditi,

3314
01:47:31,620 --> 01:47:33,580
 a prije mene to nije uradio niko 20 godina,

3315
01:47:33,580 --> 01:47:35,800
 jer nisam siguran.

3316
01:47:35,800 --> 01:47:36,640
 Zašto?

3317
01:47:36,640 --> 01:47:39,340
 Zato što nekako užužbanost grada,

3318
01:47:39,340 --> 01:47:41,140
 studij i sve te sve me nekako,

3319
01:47:41,140 --> 01:47:42,480
 nažalost,

3320
01:47:42,480 --> 01:47:43,280
 udaljilo,

3321
01:47:43,280 --> 01:47:45,060
 imao sam osnovnu molitvu,

3322
01:47:45,060 --> 01:47:46,980
 ali nisam potpuno mogao uroniti

3323
01:47:46,980 --> 01:47:49,840
 u zajedništvo sa gospodinom.

3324
01:47:50,580 --> 01:47:52,220
 i malo sam tijel mira,

3325
01:47:52,220 --> 01:47:54,700
 ispredo nisam ga gore toliko mogao pronaći.

3326
01:47:54,700 --> 01:47:56,260
 I ja sam rekao odgojitelju,

3327
01:47:56,260 --> 01:47:58,380
 aj ti mene pošalj u Međugorje ovo ljeto,

3328
01:47:58,380 --> 01:48:01,180
 pa ću ja dole malo još razmisliti,

3329
01:48:01,180 --> 01:48:02,280
 bit će sve u redu,

3330
01:48:02,280 --> 01:48:03,340
 sa ovo mi treba malo mira.

3331
01:48:03,340 --> 01:48:05,160
 I on kaže,

3332
01:48:05,160 --> 01:48:05,780
 nema problema,

3333
01:48:05,780 --> 01:48:06,360
 zlatko,

3334
01:48:06,360 --> 01:48:08,640
 možeš iduće godine sve u redu.

3335
01:48:09,420 --> 01:48:11,260
 To je bilo 2018.

3336
01:48:11,260 --> 01:48:13,640
 I ja sam otišao u Međugorje,

3337
01:48:13,640 --> 01:48:14,300
 i rekao,

3338
01:48:14,300 --> 01:48:16,180
 tamo su moji izvori,

3339
01:48:16,180 --> 01:48:18,480
 idem ja prisjetiti za tih izvora,

3340
01:48:18,480 --> 01:48:20,300
 svoga poziva,

3341
01:48:20,300 --> 01:48:20,960
 svega,

3342
01:48:20,960 --> 01:48:22,920
 da gospodin upet u meni probudi

3343
01:48:22,920 --> 01:48:25,320
 još više taj žar za njim.

3344
01:48:25,320 --> 01:48:26,820
 I tako je bilo.

3345
01:48:26,820 --> 01:48:29,760
 Iako se i tu dogodile neke napaste i sve,

3346
01:48:29,760 --> 01:48:32,740
 i sad ja sam odlučio,

3347
01:48:32,740 --> 01:48:33,660
 ok, idem,

3348
01:48:33,660 --> 01:48:35,220
 dogodneću,

3349
01:48:35,220 --> 01:48:37,540
 pološiti svoje zavijete,

3350
01:48:37,540 --> 01:48:38,900
 to vrijeme u Međugorju

3351
01:48:38,900 --> 01:48:40,000
 mi zaista bilo potrebno.

3352
01:48:40,000 --> 01:48:41,120
 I među ostalog,

3353
01:48:41,120 --> 01:48:42,520
 najvažnija stvar koja mi se dogodila,

3354
01:48:42,520 --> 01:48:43,720
 da sam ponovo,

3355
01:48:43,720 --> 01:48:44,060
 ponovo,

3356
