3624
01:55:08,600 --> 01:55:09,700
 da su stati mladi,

3625
01:55:09,700 --> 01:55:10,180
 ovaj,

3626
01:55:10,180 --> 01:55:10,640
 u Seol,

3627
01:55:10,640 --> 01:55:11,380
 2027.

3628
01:55:11,380 --> 01:55:13,460
 i okupljamo gore mlade,

3629
01:55:13,460 --> 01:55:14,260
 skupljamo ih,

3630
01:55:14,260 --> 01:55:15,640
