3631
01:55:15,640 --> 01:55:16,860
 da vidi da nisu sami,

3632
01:55:16,860 --> 01:55:17,880
 da nisu izgubljeni

3633
01:55:17,880 --> 01:55:19,000
 u ovom današnjem svijetu,

3634
01:55:19,000 --> 01:55:20,680
 koji te sve mu uči,

3635
01:55:20,680 --> 01:55:21,720
 samo ne Božijemu.

3636
01:55:22,500 --> 01:55:23,420
 Božije se odbacuje.

3637
01:55:23,420 --> 01:55:25,360
 Stoga, ljudi moji,

3638
01:55:25,360 --> 01:55:28,500
