3639
01:55:28,500 --> 01:55:29,700
 i to je moja poruka.

3640
01:55:29,700 --> 01:55:31,880
 Samo idite kristu,

3641
01:55:31,880 --> 01:55:33,880
 recept za svetost,

3642
01:55:33,880 --> 01:55:34,860
 Euharistija.

3643
01:55:34,860 --> 01:55:35,560
 Kaže,

3644
01:55:35,560 --> 01:55:36,440
 važni Karlo,

3645
01:55:36,440 --> 01:55:37,600
 kuti su skoro sveti,

3646
01:55:37,600 --> 01:55:38,380
 kaže,

3647
01:55:38,380 --> 01:55:40,940
 Euharistija je moja auto cesta za nebo.

3648
01:55:40,940 --> 01:55:42,060
 Ja to svima kažem.

3649
01:55:42,060 --> 01:55:44,060
 Jedna od najljepših rečenica,

3650
01:55:44,060 --> 01:55:45,360
 koje sam ja i prije živio,

3651
01:55:45,360 --> 01:55:46,880
 i vjerovao u to,

3652
01:55:46,880 --> 01:55:48,400
 ali na kada sam još čuo to,

3653
01:55:48,400 --> 01:55:49,180
 super,

3654
01:55:49,180 --> 01:55:49,780
 predivno.

3655
01:55:50,000 --> 01:55:50,500
 tako mlad,

3656
01:55:50,500 --> 01:55:50,920
 dečko,

3657
01:55:50,920 --> 01:55:51,720
 svetac.

3658
01:55:51,720 --> 01:55:53,960
 Najveće što me fascinira

3659
01:55:53,960 --> 01:55:55,220
 kod toga momka,

3660
01:55:55,220 --> 01:55:56,540
 je zapravo,

3661
01:55:56,540 --> 01:55:57,340
 ja u njegov godina

3662
01:55:57,340 --> 01:55:59,300
 nisam još ni bio obraćen,

3663
01:55:59,300 --> 01:56:00,960
 a on je toliko ljubio Euharistiju.

3664
01:56:00,960 --> 01:56:03,820
 Još je s toga mlad,

3665
01:56:03,820 --> 01:56:05,560
 može baš ubiti uzor mladima.

3666
01:56:05,560 --> 01:56:07,780
 Sad smo posjetili njegov grob

3667
01:56:07,780 --> 01:56:08,720
 kad smo bili u Asizu,

3668
01:56:08,720 --> 01:56:09,640
 koji se nalazi dolje,

3669
01:56:09,640 --> 01:56:11,240
 i mladi su se,

3670
01:56:11,240 --> 01:56:11,720
 vjerujem,

3671
01:56:11,720 --> 01:56:12,920
 najviše tome i oduševili.

3672
01:56:12,920 --> 01:56:14,220
 Čovjek,

3673
01:56:14,220 --> 01:56:15,420
 njihovih godina,

3674
01:56:15,420 --> 01:56:16,660
 svet,

3675
01:56:16,660 --> 01:56:17,880
 tijelo ne raspadnuto,

3676
01:56:17,880 --> 01:56:19,040
 najk tenisice,

3677
01:56:19,260 --> 01:56:19,840
 traperice,

3678
01:56:19,840 --> 01:56:22,040
 jedan zaista lijep poticaj.

3679
01:56:22,040 --> 01:56:22,360
 Evo,

3680
01:56:22,360 --> 01:56:24,280
 vidiš da se može živjeti svetost.

3681
01:56:24,280 --> 01:56:25,660
 Vidiš da svetost nije

3682
01:56:25,660 --> 01:56:26,520
