3684
01:56:28,240 --> 01:56:29,440
 Svi smo pozvani

3685
01:56:29,440 --> 01:56:31,020
 živjeti evanđelje u ponini

3686
01:56:31,020 --> 01:56:32,100
 i biti sveti.

3687
01:56:32,100 --> 01:56:32,820
 S toga,

3688
01:56:32,820 --> 01:56:33,780
 za kraj,

3689
01:56:33,780 --> 01:56:36,000
 Euharistija.

3690
01:56:36,000 --> 01:56:38,700
 Zlatko,

3691
01:56:38,700 --> 01:56:39,220
 hvala ti,

3692
01:56:39,220 --> 01:56:41,140
 hvala što si izdvojio vrijeme za nas,

3693
01:56:41,140 --> 01:56:42,420
 što si došao u goste.

3694
01:56:43,180 --> 01:56:46,940
 ponovit će možda ko Bog da nekad opet znam da ti je ovo prvo gostovanje,

3695
01:56:46,940 --> 01:56:48,400
 pa evo kad postaneš papa,

3696
01:56:48,400 --> 01:56:50,340
 ako postaneš.

3697
01:56:50,500 --> 01:56:51,500
 Hvala tebi, Marko,

3698
01:56:51,500 --> 01:56:52,300
 je na pozivu.

3699
01:56:52,300 --> 01:56:54,700
 Ne moja da budeš nedostupan tada.

3700
01:56:55,400 --> 01:56:57,520
 Vjeruj mi da je bilo ko drugi je pozvao,

3701
01:56:57,520 --> 01:56:59,620
 ne bi došao jer trema mi je,

3702
01:56:59,620 --> 01:57:00,500
