3703
01:57:00,500 --> 01:57:02,600
 ali evo ti ko moj prijatelj,

3704
01:57:02,600 --> 01:57:04,720
 nisam mogao odbiti evo.

3705
01:57:04,720 --> 01:57:06,080
 Hvala ti na pozivu.

3706
01:57:06,080 --> 01:57:07,480
 Hvala ti, evo dragi gledatari,

3707
01:57:07,480 --> 01:57:09,280
